description:
Welcome to Greenwood Automotive! A family owned and operated dealership like none other, we've been changing the way customers feel about the car buying experience since 2007. We're proud to offer the very best in quality, selection, and service. Our friendly staff will always go the extra mile to ensure that you get exactly what you need. Take this 2020 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S for example.... Offered in Guards Red exterior with Mojave Beige/Black interior, it's certain to make a great addition to your family or business! Take note of all this vehicle has to offer: Important/Valuable Packages & Equipment Premium Package ($5,380 value)
  • Seat Ventilation
  • Comfort Access
  • Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus (PDLS+)
  • Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC)
  • BOSE Surround Sound System
  • Lane Keep Assist (LKA) with Traffic Sign Recognition
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
Other Notable Features/Options Let us show you why Greenwood Automotive is the dealership you can trust. To verify availability on this or any vehicle, please contact our client care team at (303) 771-1007 or stop by see us at 18945 Twenty Mile Lane Parker CO 80134. Whether you are looking for German luxury, classic American muscle, a tough truck, or a Jeep, our friendly staff will always go the extra mile to ensure that you get exactly what you need. description:
Discover the perfect blend of performance and capability in this 2018 Chevrolet Colorado Z71. With its powerful V6 engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and 4-wheel drive, this Colorado is ready to tackle any adventure with confidence.

• CLEAN CARFAX
• ONE OWNER
• AUDIO SYSTEM FEATURE, BOSE PREMIUM 7-SPEAKER SYSTEM
• Cajun Red Tintcoat Exterior
• AUDIO SYSTEM, CHEVROLET MYLINK RADIO WITH NAVIGATION AND 8" DIAGONAL COLOR TOUCH-SCREEN
• TRAILERING PACKAGE, HEAVY-DUTY
• Power driver seat
• Remote keyless entry
• Heated Driver & Front Passenger Seats
• Alloy wheels

This Colorado Z71 is more than just a capable off-road machine – it's also packed with premium features that will elevate your driving experience. The Bose premium audio system and Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with navigation provide exceptional sound quality and intuitive connectivity. The heavy-duty trailering package makes towing a breeze, while the heated front seats and power driver's seat ensure maximum comfort no matter the journey.

Slip behind the wheel and you'll be impressed by the Colorado's smooth and responsive performance. The V6 engine delivers ample power for passing, merging, and conquering rugged terrain, while the 8-speed automatic transmission provides seamless gear changes. And with 4-wheel drive, you'll have the confidence to tackle any weather or road condition.

But the Colorado Z71 isn't just about brute force – it also offers a refined and well-appointed interior. Premium cloth and leatherette seating, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and an array of advanced safety and convenience features come together to create a truly premium driving experience.

Whether you're tackling the great outdoors or navigating the daily commute, this 2018 Chevrolet Colorado Z71 is the perfect companion. With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and exceptional value, it's a vehicle that's sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today to take this Colorado for a test drive and experience the difference for yourself.

description:
This 2018 Honda Clarity Plug-In Hybrid , has a Crystal Black Pearl exterior and Black interior color with only 0 miles. Stock Number D13350. You can connect with us by calling 515-265-1467. PRICED TO SELL! Priced so heavily discounted due to Rebuilt/Salvage title. For more information, please call dealer at (515) 265-1467. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

The 2024 Honda Accord EX offers a refined blend of sophisticated style and intelligent efficiency, finished in a sharp Solar Silver Metallic exterior. Powered by an efficient 1.5-liter turbocharged I4 engine delivering 192 horsepower and 192 lb-ft of torque, this iconic sedan provides smooth, responsive performance and exceptional fuel economy through its seamless continuously variable transmission (CVT) and confident front-wheel drive.

The well-equipped EX trim outfits the Accord with 17-inch alloy wheels, all-season touring tires, and distinctive full LED lighting. Inside, you'll find premium cloth seating surfaces with heated front seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob, and modern, minimalist interior design. The spacious and thoughtfully designed cabin offers best-in-class passenger room and versatile cargo space, along with dual-zone automatic climate control and an 8-speaker premium audio system for a comfortable daily commute.

Advanced technology features include the latest Honda Connect system with a 12.3-inch touchscreen, wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, and a Wi-Fi hotspot capability. The Accord EX also boasts the Honda Sensing suite of safety and driver-assist technologies as standard equipment, a customizable 7-inch digital instrument cluster, and available wireless phone charging for enhanced convenience and confidence on every journey.

Engineered for a perfect balance of comfort, technology, and value, this Accord achieves an impressive EPA-estimated 29 MPG city/37 MPG highway, making it an intelligent and elegant choice for the modern driver.

Audi's renowned engineering provides a composed, athletic ride that feels equally at home on Houston city streets and open highways. Precise steering and a quiet, refined cabin create a driving experience that is both dynamic and comfortable, perfect for daily commutes or weekend escapes.Inside, the cabin surrounds you with modern luxury and thoughtful design. High-quality materials, clean lines and a driver-focused layout create an environment that feels sophisticated and intuitive. Supportive seating and generous passenger space ensure comfort for everyone on board, while advanced infotainment and connectivity features keep you seamlessly connected and informed. Every detail is designed to enhance convenience, confidence and driving enjoyment.Versatility is a hallmark of the Audi Q5. Ample cargo space and flexible interior design make it easy to adapt to your lifestyle, whether you are running errands, traveling with family or heading out for adventure. Advanced safety and driver-assist technologies add peace of mind, allowing you to focus on the thrill of the drive. With its blend of luxury, performance and practicality, the 2023 Audi Q5 Premium continues to stand out in the competitive luxury SUV segment.At Audi Central Houston, it's not just our offices, customer lounges and parts and service facilities that are high tech. Equally forward-thinking is the professional, informative and friendly way we do business. With our client-centric approach, we pride ourselves in providing drivers with an entirely new way to shop for, maintain, and embrace the Audi luxury-performance tradition. Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Android Auto/Apple CarPlay smart device wireless mirroring
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Experience the Pinnacle of Adventure and Comfort with the 2025 Subaru Outback Premium

Discover the perfect balance of rugged capability and refined sophistication with the 2025 Subaru Outback Premium. This exceptional vehicle is meticulously crafted to elevate your driving experience, offering a seamless blend of advanced features and uncompromising performance.

• Collision Warning System
• Blind-Spot Monitors
• Lane Keeping Assist
• Touchscreen Controls
• Apple CarPlay
• Android Auto
• Super Clean
• One Owner Clean CarFax
• Over $5000 in Factory upgrades!
• BSD & RCTA & Keyless Access & Push Button Start
• Power Moonroof
• Hands-Free Power Rear Gate
• Radio: Subaru 11.6" Multimedia System with Navigation
• Keyless Access with Push Button Start

Powered by a robust 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine and Lineartronic CVT transmission, the Outback Premium delivers an impressive balance of efficiency and capability. With standard Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, you'll conquer any terrain with confidence, while the impressive fuel economy of 26 city/32 highway MPG ensures you can explore further without frequent stops.

Beyond its exceptional performance, the Outback Premium is meticulously designed to provide the ultimate in comfort and convenience. The spacious and well-appointed interior features premium cloth upholstery, heated front seats, and a host of advanced technologies, including the intuitive 11.6-inch Multimedia Plus System with Navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration.

Safety is also a top priority, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features, including Blind Spot Detection, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Collision Warning System. These cutting-edge systems work seamlessly to help you navigate the road with confidence and peace of mind.

Whether you're embarking on a weekend adventure or tackling your daily commute, the 2025 Subaru Outback Premium is the perfect companion. With its unparalleled combination of capability, technology, and comfort, this exceptional vehicle is sure to exceed your expectations and elevate your driving experience to new heights.

We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the 2025 Subaru Outback Premium for yourself. Let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can transform the way you explore the world around you. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be captivated by its unrivaled blend of performance, versatility, and sophistication.

This Certified 2025 BMW X5 xDrive40i, has a Black Sapphire Metallic exterior and a Black interior color. 10,480 miles. Stock Number B9440. You can connect with us by calling 765-449-2892 No Accidents! One Owner! Important Package and Feature Information Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless Apple CarPlay and Wireless Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description: This 2021 Porsche 911 Carrera Cabriolet is a uniquely spec'd example sourced specifically for its rare combination of Racing Yellow over a Slate Gray/Chalk leather interior with a Blue cabriolet roof - an eye-catching trio that sets it apart from nearly every other 992 on the road. Ordered with the highly desirable Premium Package, it brings BOSE Surround Sound, ventilated front seats, PDLS+ headlights, Surround View, Lane Change Assist, and ambient lighting, making top-down driving both luxurious and effortless. The Sport Chrono Package and black Sport Tailpipes add performance character, while the 20"/21" Carrera Classic wheels and Racing Yellow-accented tachometer, stopwatch, and seat belts tie the entire aesthetic together with purpose and flair. This particular car was selected after an enthusiast meticulously searched for a 911 that wasn't just well-equipped, but truly special - a build that felt tailored rather than typical. When this Cabriolet appeared, its condition and specification made it clear it was the one worth pursuing. Today it stands as a beautifully preserved, tastefully optioned 911 that blends performance, luxury, and personality in a way few examples do.

This 2021 Kia Soul LX, has a Snow White Pearl exterior and a Black interior. 68,342 miles. Stock Number M7759616A. You can connect with us by calling (937) 240-1310. No Accidents! Important Package and Feature Information Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
In-car Entertainment
  • Touchscreen - flat out convenient. Say goodbye to the twists and turns of your daily drive...we're talking about buttons and knobs of course! Touchscreen allows you to control certain features with your fingertips, making it easy to use while also providing information at a glance. With touchscreen, your fingerprints will be all over your drive.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Vehicle Details
Discover exceptional value with this 2023 Nissan Pathfinder Platinum, now available in Lewisburg, WV. This premium 4WD SUV features a robust 3.5L V6 gasoline engine and a clean 27,546-mile odometer — low mileage for a 2023, offering years of reliable performance and strong resale potential. Priced to move, this Nissan Pathfinder Platinum represents the best price in the area for its class and condition. Inside, refined Platinum-level appointments meet advanced technology. Enjoy seamless connectivity with Apple CarPlay and hands-free Bluetooth, and stay on track with integrated Navigation. The heated steering wheel adds comfort during colder months, while the Back-Up Camera enhances safety and visibility when reversing or parking. Built for confident driving in diverse conditions, the 4WD system pairs with the V6 powerplant to deliver smooth acceleration and capable handling whether you're commuting, hauling gear, or heading off the beaten path. Practical features and thoughtful luxury make this Nissan Pathfinder an ideal choice for families and active lifestyles. Located in Lewisburg, WV, this 2023 Nissan Pathfinder Platinum offers an outstanding combination of low miles, high specification, and competitive pricing. Contact us today to arrange a test drive or to request more details — experience why this Nissan Pathfinder represents one of the smartest SUV buys available in the region.

Equipment
Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. Start this 2023 Nissan Pathfinder from inside with remote start. Good News! This certified CARFAX 1-owner vehicle has only had one owner before you. Bluetooth technology is built into this model, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. This mid-size suv offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. The leather seats in this unit are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. Protect this mid-size suv from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system. This Nissan Pathfinder is pure luxury with a heated steering wheel. Engulf yourself with the crystal clear sound of a BOSE sound system in this model. This vehicle offers Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. The installed navigation system will keep you on the right path.

Powered by a robust 3.3L V6 engine paired with a smooth 5-speed automatic transmission, this front-wheel drive beauty is ready to hit the road. Its front/rear independent MacPherson strut suspension ensures a comfortable ride, while the pwr 4-wheel disc brakes provide precise stopping power. Inside, you'll find a convenient center console, tilt/telescopic steering wheel with audio controls, and a multi-information display to keep you informed. description: . The 2007 Mercedes-Benz CLK350 2dr Cabriolet is an exemplary blend of performance and luxury, epitomizing the brand’s timeless design philosophy. Underneath its elegantly sculpted hood lies a robust 3.5L V6 engine that delivers an exhilarating driving experience with a smooth combination of power and responsiveness. The vehicle’s sophisticated engineering ensures excellent handling dynamics, making both city and highway drives a pleasure. Externally, the CLK350 radiates classic Mercedes-Benz elegance with its refined lines and graceful proportions, capturing attention at every turn. The retractable soft-top seamlessly integrates into the vehicle's design, allowing for open-air driving bliss whenever desired. Inside, the cabriolet boasts a tastefully appointed interior, featuring premium materials and meticulous craftsmanship that offer unparalleled comfort and style. High-quality finishes and state-of-the-art technology ensure a luxurious driving experience, complete with creature comforts expected from a high-end vehicle. Safety and innovation are at the forefront of the CLK350, with a suite of features designed to provide peace of mind on every journey. Advanced safety systems, including stability and traction control, work in tandem to enhance road safety in various driving conditions. Additionally, the car is equipped with modern amenities like a premium sound system and an intuitive infotainment interface, elevating every drive to a higher echelon of enjoyment. The 2007 Mercedes-Benz CLK350 2dr Cabriolet is not just a car, but an experience that embodies the spirit of sophisticated driving pleasure. description: Discover the 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR, a stylish and reliable sedan that combines modern technology with impressive performance. Finished in sleek Super Black Clearcoat, this used vehicle offers a sporty yet refined look that turns heads. With 141,056 miles on the odometer, it’s been well-maintained and features a spacious interior with the Sport trim, designed for comfort and excitement. Powered by a 2.5-liter four-cylinder engine delivering 188 horsepower and 180 lb-ft of torque, this Altima provides an engaging drive with excellent fuel efficiency—27 mpg city and 37 mpg highway. Its CVT with Xtronic transmission ensures smooth acceleration, while front-wheel drive offers confident handling. Inside, the cabin is equipped with advanced tech features including Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, a backup camera, blind spot monitor, collision warning, cross traffic alert, keyless entry, push start, and satellite radio readiness, making every drive safer and more connected. The 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR also emphasizes safety with advanced features designed to protect and assist. It is equipped with automatic emergency braking at the rear, providing crucial collision prevention. The rear check rear seat reminder helps ensure no one is left behind, while dual front knee airbags offer additional crash protection. Rear parking sensors assist with precise maneuvering, complemented by four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) for stability. The vehicle includes anti-lockout power door locks to prevent lock-ins, cornering brake control for better handling, and auto-locking power door locks, all contributing to a secure driving experience. Entertainment and technology are key highlights of the Altima. It features NissanConnect compatibility for seamless app integration, allowing control of navigation, music, and more. Hands-free voice-operated calling and radio functions improve convenience, while the 8-inch infotainment touchscreen provides easy access to audio and vehicle settings. The six-speaker system delivers quality sound, with auxiliary inputs for USB and iPod/iPhone devices. Electronic messaging assistance with read and voice functions ensures staying connected is safe and effortless during your drive. Performance is further enhanced by a tuned sport suspension, designed to improve handling and provide a dynamic driving experience. This setup enhances stability and responsiveness, making the Altima 2.5 SR suitable for both daily commuting and spirited driving. Whether navigating city streets or open highways, this sedan offers a blend of reliability, comfort, and fun that appeals to drivers seeking a versatile vehicle. 2020 Nissan Altima Safety and Security Features This model includes automatic emergency braking at the rear, providing vital collision prevention. The rear check rear seat reminder ensures no passengers or valuables are left behind. Dual front knee airbags offer added crash protection, while rear parking sensors assist with tight spaces. Four-wheel ABS enhances braking stability, and anti-lockout power door locks prevent accidental lock-ins. Cornering brake control improves handling around curves, and auto-locking power door locks add security, making this Altima a safe choice for daily use. 2020 Nissan Altima Entertainment and Technology Features The Altima’s tech features include NissanConnect compatibility for app integration, enabling navigation, music, and other functions. Hands-free voice-operated calls and radio enhance ease of use, while the 8-inch touchscreen displays all essential info clearly. The six-speaker audio system delivers quality sound, supported by auxiliary inputs for USB and iPod/iPhone. Electronic messaging assistance with read and voice functions helps keep you connected safely on the go. This 1999 Plymouth Prowler comes equipped with a range of features designed to enhance your driving experience. The advanced 10-speed automatic transmission provides smooth, efficient power delivery, while the hybrid system delivers an impressive 22 city/24 highway mpg.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, this F-150 is packed with premium features that elevate your driving experience. The spacious cabin offers comfortable cloth seating, dual-zone climate control, and a premium B&O sound system to keep you entertained on the road. The Intelligent Access with Push Button Start and Remote Start System make your daily routine more convenient, while the Ford BlueCruise semi-autonomous driving technology gives you the confidence to tackle long hauls with ease.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Adaptive Cruise Control, Blind Spot Monitoring, and a comprehensive suite of airbags to protect you and your passengers. description:
Discover the perfect blend of capability and comfort in the 2024 Toyota Tacoma SR. This rugged midsize pickup is engineered to take on any adventure, while delivering a refined driving experience that will impress even the most discerning driver.

Boasting a host of impressive features, the Tacoma SR is equipped to handle your toughest tasks. Equipped with a powerful 2.4L 4-cylinder engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, this 4WD truck delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 19 city/24 highway MPG.

• 8" Toyota Audio Multimedia System
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Rear Window Defroster
• Power Windows and Locks
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• Traction Control
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes
• Anti-Lock Braking System
• Dual Front and Side Impact Airbags
• Overhead Airbag
• Rear View Camera

The Tacoma SR's impressive capabilities are matched by its refined interior, featuring comfortable fabric seating, a spacious front center armrest, and a split-folding rear seat for added versatility. Thoughtful touches like the illuminated entry, outside temperature display, and telescoping steering wheel ensure a premium driving experience.

Designed to tackle the toughest terrain, the Tacoma SR's rugged good looks are enhanced by its 17" steel wheels, body-color bumpers, and rear step bumper. The heated power side mirrors and automatic headlights add a touch of convenience, while the variably intermittent wipers keep you driving safely in any weather.

With its uncompromising performance, versatile features, and timeless design, the 2024 Toyota Tacoma SR is the ultimate companion for your next adventure. Experience the difference for yourself by visiting our showroom and taking this remarkable truck for a test drive. We're confident you'll be impressed by its capabilities and confident in your decision to make it your own.

At our dealership, we're dedicated to providing exceptional customer service and ensuring you drive away in the perfect vehicle for your needs. Let us show you why the Tacoma SR is the smart choice for your next pickup. Visit us today and let's discuss how this impressive truck can enhance your driving experience.

Premium Package

Experience the perfect blend of luxury and performance with the 2019 Mercedes-Benz C-Class C 300. This stunning sedan, finished in a sleek Polar White exterior, exudes elegance and sophistication, making every drive a statement. Under the hood, the powerful 2.0L 4-cylinder engine delivers an impressive 255 horsepower, ensuring a thrilling ride whether you're navigating city streets or cruising on the highway. Inside, you'll find a beautifully appointed Magma Grey interior featuring premium leather seating, automatic climate control, and a state-of-the-art audio system that elevates your driving experience. With advanced technology like Bluetooth connectivity, a backup camera, and parking sensors, this C 300 is designed for both comfort and convenience. Dont miss your chance to own this exceptional vehicle—come in for a test drive today!

This Mercedes-Benz C 300 is equipped with a variety of features including MP3 compatibility, USB ports, keyless entry, Sirius Satellite Radio, side airbags, power seats, tire pressure monitoring, premium wheels, and LED headlights. It also boasts a power liftgate/trunk and projector headlamps, ensuring you have everything you need for a safe and enjoyable ride.

At Hartsville Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Fiat, we provide a trusted destination for quality vehicles and expert automotive care in the heart of Hartsville, South Carolina. Whether you're shopping for a hardworking truck, a family SUV, or a performance-driven ride, our team is here to help you drive home with confidence.

This 2017 Toyota Tacoma Limited V6 is a versatile and capable pickup that's ready to take on any adventure. Boasting a powerful V6 engine, 4-wheel drive, and a tow package, this Tacoma is built to handle tough jobs with ease. Standout features include:

• Navigation System
• Entune App Suite
• Premium JBL Audio System
• Automatic Temperature Control
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• Power Moonroof
• Rear Parking Camera
• Leather Seat Trim

The Tacoma's rugged good looks are complemented by its impressive fuel efficiency, delivering 18 MPG in the city and 23 MPG on the highway. With 80,130 miles on the odometer, this well-maintained truck still has plenty of life left to offer.

Slip behind the wheel and you'll appreciate the Tacoma's comfortable, well-appointed cabin. The leather-trimmed seats provide a premium feel, while the intuitive technology features keep you connected and entertained on the road. And with the available tow package, you can haul your toys or gear with confidence.

Whether you're tackling work projects, exploring the great outdoors, or simply commuting in style, this 2017 Toyota Tacoma Limited V6 is a versatile and capable companion. Experience the power, capability, and refinement for yourself by scheduling a test drive today.

Serving Hartsville, Florence, Darlington, and the entire Pee Dee region, Hartsville Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram Fiat offers one of South Carolina's best selections of new and used vehicles. Our dealership is dedicated to providing reliable service, competitive pricing, and a customer-focused experience from start to finish.

Inside, the cabin is outfitted with premium leather-trimmed bucket seats, offering both comfort and style. The Reverse Sensing System and Trailer Brake Controller make it easy to maneuver and tow with confidence, while the SYNC voice-activated communication and entertainment system keeps you connected on the go.

With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and striking appearance, this 2014 Ford F-150 FX4 is the perfect choice for the discerning truck buyer. description: Explore the Hyundai Tucson SEL w/ Convenience Package, a versatile and reliable SUV designed to meet your needs on the road. This multipurpose passenger vehicle boasts a striking exterior color in sleek gray, complementing its bold and contemporary style. With a model year of 2023, this vehicle ensures a modern driving experience while maintaining a classic appeal.Equipped with a robust 2.5-liter engine and a 4-cylinder configuration from HMC, the Tucson SEL AWD delivers a smooth and efficient performance tailored for various driving scenarios. Its 4-wheel drive system provides enhanced traction and control, making it a suitable choice for navigating Colorado's diverse terrain and weather conditions.Safety is paramount in the Tucson, with standard features including ABS, Blind Spot Intervention, Blind Spot Monitoring, Lane Departure Warning, and a comprehensive airbag system covering multiple locations within the vehicle. The SEL trim also offers additional safety enhancements like Automatic Emergency Braking for pedestrians in case of sudden hazards.Inside the cabin, comfort and convenience take center stage with a spacious 5-seat arrangement and the SEL w/ Convenience Package. Enjoy modern amenities such as Keyless Ignition, a Direct Tire Pressure Monitoring System, and a Rear Cross Traffic Alert system for added peace of mind while driving.The Tucson seamlessly combines practicality with style, offering a balance of functionality and aesthetics. With a versatile 2-row seating layout and ample cargo space, this SUV accommodates diverse lifestyles and transportation needs. The upscale trim level ensures that you experience the right mix of luxury and performance every time you take the wheel.Visit Schomp Hyundai in Aurora to experience the innovative features and exceptional quality of the Hyundai Tucson SEL first-hand. Trust in our commitment to providing a transparent and customer-centric car-buying experience, where you can find the ideal vehicle that suits your preferences and lifestyle with ease. Our knowledgeable staff is dedicated to assisting you throughout your journey to find the perfect Hyundai SUV for your adventures in Denver and beyond.

Experience the power and capability of the 2021 Nissan Titan SV 4x4. This impressive truck is ready to take on any challenge, with its robust 5.6L V8 engine delivering an exceptional 400 horsepower and 4-wheel drive system for unparalleled off-road performance.

Key features include:
• 1-Owner Vehicle
• Fletcher Inspected and Approved
• Local Trade-In
• SV Convenience Package
• Accessory Utility Package
• Off-Road Protection Package
• Radio: NissanConnect with Navigation
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Rear HVAC Vents
• 110V/12V Outlets in Back of Center Console
• Chrome Interior Door Locks
• Intelligent Key System
• Remote Engine Start

This Titan SV is more than just a workhorse – it's a premium-level pickup that offers the latest technology and creature comforts to make every drive a pleasure. The 9-inch touchscreen display with built-in navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and informed, while the heated front captain's chairs and power-adjustable driver's seat provide exceptional comfort.

Enhance your adventures with the Accessory Utility Package, which includes a handy bumper step and trailer hitch, and the Off-Road Protection Package with all-season floor mats and other rugged accessories. The SV Convenience Package further elevates your experience with features like auto-dimming rearview mirror, front and rear parking sensors, and the impressive Nissan door-to-door navigation system.

With its striking white exterior and well-appointed interior, this 2021 Nissan Titan SV 4x4 is a true standout in the full-size truck segment. Its impressive fuel efficiency, with 21 mpg on the highway, makes it a practical choice for both work and play.

Don't miss your chance to experience the power, capability, and premium features of this exceptional Titan. Schedule a test drive today and let us show you why this truck is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

Elevate your driving experience with the remarkable 2020 Ram 1500 Laramie. This powerful and versatile full-size pickup offers an unbeatable combination of performance, technology, and premium comfort, making it the ultimate choice for discerning truck enthusiasts.

• HEMI 5.7L V8 Multi Displacement VVT Engine

Engineered to conquer any terrain, the 2020 Ram 1500 Laramie is powered by the legendary HEMI 5.7L V8 engine, delivering impressive performance and efficiency. The 8-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive system provide seamless power delivery and unparalleled capability, whether you're tackling challenging off-road conditions or navigating the daily commute.

Step inside the cabin and experience the epitome of luxury. The premium leather-trimmed bucket seats offer exceptional comfort and support, while the Uconnect 4 infotainment system with an 8.4" touchscreen display puts a world of connectivity and entertainment at your fingertips. Stay comfortable in any weather with the heated and ventilated front seats, and enjoy the convenience of the heated steering wheel.

Packed with advanced safety and driver-assistance technologies, the 2020 Ram 1500 Laramie keeps you and your loved ones secure on the road. Features like the ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera, Electronic Stability Control, and Brake Assist provide added peace of mind, ensuring you can navigate with confidence.

2019 Ford F 150 XL 4WD Standard Cab Low Miles EcoBoost Power

Under the hood, the 2.7L EcoBoost V6 paired with a 10 speed automatic transmission delivers strong performance and efficiency, while four wheel drive, an electronic locking rear differential with 3.73 axle ratio, and the payload package with 6,800 pound GVWR make it ready for tough jobs and changing conditions.

Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • A head-up display projects gauge (speed, RPM, etc.) information onto the inside of the windshield just below the driver's line of sight.
  • Brake assist senses panic braking from the speed of the brake pedal's travel and applies all available power brake boost.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

description: At Schomp Nissan, we take pride in offering exceptional pre-owned vehicles, including the 2008 Nissan Altima in a stunning Silver color. As a CarFax Top-Rated Dealer, we uphold our commitment to providing outstanding customer service and a transparent buying experience through our innovative approach of One Price. One Person. One Hour.®The Nissan Altima is a high-quality coupe that has been meticulously inspected to meet our stringent standards of quality and reliability. With a 2.5-liter, 4-cylinder engine producing 170 horsepower, this vehicle is designed to offer both efficiency and performance. The engine model QR25DE ensures a smooth driving experience, while the Dual Overhead Cam (DOHC) valve train design enhances engine efficiency.Safety is a top priority, with 1st Row driver and passenger airbags, as well as various advanced safety features such as Direct Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS) and Manual seat belts for all occupants. This Altima model is a 4x2 drive type, making it suitable for varied driving conditions.Inside, the Nissan Altima boasts a comfortable and spacious interior with two doors, suitable for couples or small families. The vehicle's odometer shows 61,824 miles, and its Next Service Date is not specified. The MPGs stand at 23 city and 31 highway, offering a balance of fuel efficiency and performance.With our stress-free buying process and dedication to meeting your individual needs, Schomp Nissan invites you to visit our dealership and discover the perfect used car to complement your lifestyle. Our knowledgeable team is ready to assist you in finding the ideal vehicle to suit your needs.Please contact us for more details on the available equipment and features of this distinctive 2008 Nissan Altima before making your purchase.

2026 Volvo XC40 B5 Plus AWD Cloud VOLVO CERTIFIED!!, Dial the Dealer Direct ...Call Paul, or text 240-731-0977, Experience the perfect blend of Scandinavian luxury and sustainable performance with this Certified Pre-Owned 2026 Volvo XC40 B5 AWD Plus. Finished in stunning Cloud Blue over a Charcoal interior, this mild-hybrid SUV is the ideal companion for navigating the streets of Bethesda, MD, and the greater Washington DC area. Powered by a 2.0L Turbo-Charged engine with a 48V mild-hybrid system, it delivers a responsive 247 HP while maximizing efficiency through regenerative braking. Whether you are commuting into the District or heading out for a weekend in Northern Virginia, the standard All-Wheel Drive ensures confident handling in all weather conditions., Inside, the XC40 Plus trim offers a sanctuary of high-tech convenience and premium comfort. This model features the highly sought-after Google built-in system, providing seamless access to Google Maps, Google Assistant, and the Play Store directly on the 12.3-inch digital display. Local drivers will appreciate the Laminated Panoramic Sunroof, 360-degree Surround View Camera, and the Climate Package, which includes heated front seats for those chilly Maryland mornings. The versatile cargo area is enhanced with a folding load floor and grocery bag holders, making trips to the Bethesda Row shops or the local market easier than ever., Safety remains at the heart of the Volvo experience, and this 2026 model is equipped with the latest driver-assistance technology. You will find peace of mind on the Capital Beltway with features like Blind Spot Information System (BLIS) with Steer Assist, Lane Keeping Aid, and Collision Mitigation. This vehicle also includes the upgraded Pixel Technology Headlights for superior nighttime visibility and Adaptive Cruise Control to take the stress out of DC traffic. With a 3.8 gallons per 100 miles efficiency rating and a suite of sensors protecting every angle, it is one of the safest and most intelligent compact luxury SUVs on the road today., Choosing a Certified Pre-Owned Volvo means you benefit from a rigorous 170-point inspection and an extended factory-backed warranty. This XC40 comes with the remainder of the 4-year/50,000-mile limited warranty, plus the added protection of the Volvo Certified program, which includes 24/7 Roadside Assistance and a 1-year subscription to the Volvo Cars Remote App. Proudly serving residents in Bethesda, Chevy Chase, and across the Washington DC metro area, this Cloud Blue XC40 B5 AWD represents a rare opportunity to own a near-new luxury hybrid with incredible value and world-class safety., All-Wheel Drive, Panoramic Sunroof, Leather Seats, 360 Camera, Google Built-in, Apple CarPlay, Adaptive Cruise Control, Heated Front Seats, Blind Spot Information System (BLIS), Mild Hybrid, 19-inch Alloy Wheels, Power Tailgate, Keyless Entry, Remote Start, Climate Package, LED Headlights, Lane Keeping Aid, Wireless Smartphone Charging, Park Assist, Premium Sound System.. description:
2021 MERCEDES-BENZ AMG GT BLACK SERIES

BURMESTER HIGH END SOUND SYSTEM, MATTE CARBON CROSSBAR, LANE TRACKING PACKAGE, AND MORE!

OVERVIEW
The 2021 Mercedes-AMG GT Black Series is the result of an uncompromising fusion of motorsport technology, aerodynamic mastery, and handcrafted power. Under the long sculpted hood lies a re-engineered 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 with a flat-plane crankshaft, producing 720 horsepower and 590 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a 7-speed dual-clutch transmission and rear-wheel drive, the GT Black Series accelerates from 0-60 mph in just 3.1 seconds and reaches a top speed of 202 mph. Power delivery is instantaneous, linear, and ferocious. The Black Series name is reserved for the rarest and most focused AMG models, and this GT wears it proudly. Its carbon-fiber bodywork and a massive adjustable rear wing generate track-level downforce. A race-derived coil-over suspension with adaptive damping, carbon-ceramic brakes, and Michelin Pilot Sport Cup 2 R tires ensure razor-sharp handling and unshakeable grip. Inside, the GT Black Series remains unapologetically driver-focused. Lightweight AMG Performance bucket seats, Alcantara upholstery, carbon-fiber trim, and silver contrast stitching set the tone for serious performance. The AMG digital cockpit and infotainment interface keep vital information front and center, while creature comforts like dual-zone climate control and Burmester premium audio make it surprisingly livable when the helmet comes off. Born on the racetrack, bred by AMG's most obsessive engineers, and built in limited numbers, the 2021 Mercedes-AMG GT Black Series represents the peak of Mercedes performance. For collectors and purists alike, it's one of the most extraordinary and capable front-engine supercars of the modern era.

description:
2024 Porsche 911/992 Carrera S

- One Owner
- Florida Car
- 3.0L Twin Turbo H6
- 443 Horsepower
- 8 Speed PDK Gearbox
- White over Black
- Staggered (Front 20-inch/Rear 21-inch) Carrera Classic Wheels
- 18 Way Adaptive Sport Seats
- Power Sunroof
- Sport Exhaust
- Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus
- Burmester Surround Sound System
- CarFax Accident Professionally Repaired
- Always Dealer Serviced
- 2,146 MilesThe 2024 Porsche 911/992 Carrera S represents the perfect blend of timeless design and cutting-edge performance, staying true to the 911's legendary DNA while pushing the limits of modern engineering. This one-owner Florida car has been meticulously maintained since new and shows only 2,146 miles, presenting in stunning condition throughout. Finished in classic White over a refined Black leather interior, it captures the essence of understated performance and sophistication that defines Porsches most iconic model.Under the rear decklid sits a potent 3.0-liter twin-turbocharged flat-six engine producing 443 horsepower, paired to Porsche's lightning-fast 8-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission. The combination delivers breathtaking acceleration and razor-sharp shifts, offering an exceptional driving experience whether on the highway or the backroads. The Carrera S's balanced chassis and rear-engine layout provide impeccable handling, while the sport exhaust system enhances the car's character with an aggressive, unmistakable Porsche soundtrack.Visually, this 992 Carrera S commands attention with its sleek silhouette and staggered 20-inch front and 21-inch rear Carrera Classic wheels that emphasize its athletic stance. The power sunroof adds an open-air element to the driving experience, while Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus ensures optimal visibility and a distinctive lighting signature. Every line and curve serves both an aesthetic and aerodynamic purpose, reinforcing the car's functional beauty.Inside, the cabin exemplifies Porsche's commitment to craftsmanship and driver-focused ergonomics. The 18-way adaptive sport seats provide exceptional comfort and support, while the Burmester surround sound system delivers concert-quality audio for every drive. Premium materials and precise detailing create an environment that feels luxurious yet purposeful, inviting both spirited driving and relaxed cruising.This example has been consistently dealer-serviced and remains in exceptional condition, with a professionally repaired CarFax-reported incident that was completed to exacting standards. For those seeking a nearly new 992 Carrera S that combines modern performance, advanced technology, and timeless style, this Porsche stands out as an outstanding opportunity to experience the very best of the brand's latest evolution.

Welcome to Dean Carter Chevrolet! We're out to change the way you feel about the car buying experience, and proud to offer our local communities in Monroe County the very best in quality, price, selection, and service. Take this 2021 Chevrolet Malibu Premier for example. Offered in Northsky Blue Metallic exterior with Dark Atmosphere/Light Wheat interior, will make a great addition to your family or business! Be sure to take note of all this vehicle has to offer: No Accidents! One Owner! Important/Valuable Packages & Equipment Enhanced Driver Confidence Package ($2,095 value)
  • Electronic Parking Brake
  • Adaptive Cruise Control
  • IntelliBeam Automatic High-Beam On/off
  • Following Distance Indicator
  • Forward Collision Alert
  • Rear Cross Traffic Alert
  • Automatic Parking Assist
  • Enhanced Automatic Emergency Braking
  • Lane Keep Assist with Lane Departure Warning
  • Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert
  • Front Pedestrian Braking
Preferred Equipment Group 2LZ
    Convenience
    • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
    Other Notable Features/Options To verify availability of this vehicle please contact our client care team at 570-992-0200 or stop by see us at 1476 Route 209 Brodheadsville PA 18322. Let us show you why Dean Carter Chevrolet is the dealership you can trust...now and in the future.

description:
Experience the thrill of the open road in this stunning 2021 Chevrolet Camaro 1LT. With its sleek, aerodynamic design and powerful 2.0L Turbocharged engine, this sports car is engineered to deliver an exhilarating driving experience.

Key features include:
• RS Package with dark tint LED tail lamps, RS-specific grilles, Black front and rear bowties, and decklid-mounted lip spoiler
• 20" 5-split spoke premium Gray-painted, machined-face aluminum wheels
• Front License Plate Bracket

This Camaro is equipped with a host of advanced technologies to enhance your driving enjoyment, including the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 System with SiriusXM Radio, Bluetooth connectivity, and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration. The premium audio system with 6 speakers ensures you'll enjoy every mile with crisp, clear sound.

For your comfort and convenience, the Camaro 1LT offers features like automatic climate control, power driver's seat, and remote keyless entry. Safety is also a priority, with advanced airbags, anti-lock brakes, and electronic stability control to give you peace of mind on the road.

Combining bold style, exhilarating performance, and cutting-edge technology, this 2021 Chevrolet Camaro 1LT is the perfect sports car for the driver who demands the best. Experience the thrill for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We look forward to helping you find the perfect vehicle to suit your needs and lifestyle.

Prices does not include Document fees, Tax, License or dealer added accessories.

description:
CERTIFIED! Discover the perfect blend of style, capability, and technology in this certified pre-owned 2024 Volkswagen Tiguan 2.0T SE. With its sleek gray exterior and well-equipped interior, this Tiguan is ready to elevate your driving experience.

This Tiguan comes equipped with a host of premium features, including:

• Roof Rack Base Carrier Bars (Set of 2)
• Wheel Splash Guards (Set of 4)
• 2-Row Carpeted MojoMats (Set of 4)

The 2.0L TSI DOHC engine, paired with an 8-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic and Volkswagen's advanced AWD system, delivers a confident and responsive performance, while the impressive fuel efficiency of 22 city/29 highway MPG ensures you can go the distance.

Inside, you'll find a wealth of comfort and convenience features, such as dual-zone automatic climate control, a power driver's seat, and a premium audio system with SiriusXM. The Tiguan's roomy interior and versatile cargo space make it the perfect companion for your everyday adventures and weekend getaways.

As a Volkswagen Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this Tiguan has undergone a rigorous 100+ point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty, roadside assistance, and a vehicle history report. You can drive with confidence, knowing that this Tiguan has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide you with years of reliable service.

Experience the exceptional value and peace of mind that comes with this certified pre-owned 2024 Volkswagen Tiguan 2.0T SE. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable SUV can enhance your driving lifestyle.

This 2016 Ram 1500 Big Horn features a spacious crew cab, durable bed and towing-ready chassis — ideal for contractors, weekend adventurers, and families who need strength and utility. The V8 5.7L engine delivers impressive towing capacity and highway cruising power while the 4WD system provides traction on snow, mud, and rough terrain. Don't miss this opportunity to own a dependable, feature-packed Ram 1500 Big Horn in Red Lion PA at the best price around. Schedule a test drive today and experience the blend of muscle, comfort, and modern convenience that makes this truck a smart value. Clean CARFAX confirms its quality — act now.

Never get into a cold vehicle again with the remote start feature on this vehicle. The Ram 1500 offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. The Ram 1500 is pure luxury with a heated steering wheel. Bluetooth technology is built into this 1/2 ton pickup, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. 2023 BENTLEY BENTAYGA EWB AZURE

TOURING SPECIFICATION, NAIM FOR BENTLEY SOUND SYSTEM, POWER CLOSE REAR DOORS, & MORE!

OVERVIEW
Experience peak modern luxury SUV design with the 2023 Bentley Bentayga Azure––a bold statement in craftsmanship, comfort, and quiet power. This Extended Wheelbase (EWB) flagship offers an opulent rear-cabin experience that rivals executive sedans, while delivering the commanding presence and all-terrain confidence the Bentayga is renowned for. Under the hood, a 4.0L twin-turbocharged V8 produces a stout 542 horsepower and 568 lb-ft of torque, paired to an 8-speed automatic transmission and Bentley's advanced all-wheel-drive system. Whether you're cruising quietly through the city or unleashing power on open roads, the Bentayga EWB Azure delivers a refined yet responsive drive––with four-wheel steering and Bentley Dynamic Ride for remarkable agility and comfort. Craftsmanship and high-quality materials like Nappa leather and Piano Black Veneer take priority in the Bentayga's cabin, with the added benefits of advanced technology for the driver's convenience. Premium options include a Naim sound system, the Touring Specification, and illuminated diamond patterns in the doors. The 2023 Bentayga EWB Azure isn't just one of the most refined SUVs ever––it's a mobile grand suite, crafted for those who demand the highest levels of luxury, space, and sophistication.

Discover the ultimate combination of power, capability, and style with the 2025 Toyota Tacoma SR5. This exceptional midsize truck is ready to elevate your driving experience and tackle any adventure with unparalleled confidence.

Boasting a robust 2.4L 4-Cylinder engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and 4-Wheel Drive, the Tacoma SR5 delivers exceptional performance and off-road prowess. Indulge in the convenience of features such as:

• Remote Keyless Entry
• Traction Control
• ABS Brakes
• Low Tire Pressure Warning
• Electronic Stability Control
• Heated Door Mirrors
• Illuminated Entry
• Alloy Wheels

Step inside and immerse yourself in the well-appointed interior, where comfort and technology seamlessly converge. Enjoy the premium sound system, intuitive infotainment, and seamless smartphone integration with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The Tacoma SR5 also offers a host of advanced safety features, including Rear Camera, Automatic High Beams, and Front Fog Lights, ensuring your peace of mind on every journey.

Designed to tackle the toughest terrain, the Tacoma SR5 boasts a rugged exterior that combines bold styling with exceptional functionality. The powerful 4-Wheel Drive system, combined with the vehicle's advanced suspension and off-road-ready features, make it the perfect companion for your outdoor adventures, whether you're navigating winding mountain roads or traversing challenging terrain.

With its impressive towing capacity and versatile cargo bed, the Tacoma SR5 is the ultimate work-hard, play-hard companion. Whether you're hauling heavy loads, transporting your gear, or simply enjoying the great outdoors, this truck is built to handle it all with ease and confidence.

Experience the uncompromising capability and refined sophistication of the 2025 Toyota Tacoma SR5. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can transform your driving experience. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be convinced that the Tacoma SR5 is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

2021 Chevrolet Colorado LT 4WD 8-Speed Automatic V6
****
Experience the exceptional performance and versatility of the 2021 Chevrolet Colorado LT. This rugged mid-size truck is designed to conquer any terrain, offering a commanding presence on the road and the capability to tackle your toughest tasks.

Key features of this Colorado LT include:
• V6 engine with 8-speed automatic transmission and 4WD
• Impressive fuel efficiency with 17 city/24 highway MPG
• Spacious and well-appointed interior with premium audio system
• Convenient technology features like Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and a Rear Vision Camera
• Robust safety systems including ABS brakes, Dual front airbags, and Electronic Stability Control

The Colorado LT's powerful V6 engine and 4WD system deliver the performance you need to confidently navigate city streets, winding backroads, and challenging off-road conditions. With a towing capacity of up to 7,000 lbs., this truck can easily handle your gear, equipment, or trailer, making it the ideal companion for your active lifestyle.

Inside, the Colorado LT offers a comfortable and well-equipped cabin, with features like a 6-speaker audio system, power driver's seat, and steering wheel-mounted controls to keep you in command. The Rear Vision Camera and available safety technologies provide added peace of mind, allowing you to maneuver with confidence in any situation.

Whether you're tackling a job site, exploring the great outdoors, or simply commuting in style, the 2021 Chevrolet Colorado LT is the versatile and capable truck that can handle it all. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Colorado LT's uncompromising performance and refined design.

Convenience
  • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

Now with hands-off cruise control with lane change simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles with minimal steering input from you.   • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.

  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

description:
This Copper Crest 2024 Lexus RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV is a bold and exciting choice for anyone who loves a mix of power and efficiency. With its unique hybrid turbocharged engine and all-wheel drive, it offers a smooth yet thrilling ride. You can drive with total confidence knowing this RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV has a clean, one owner CARFAX history. It is a modern, high-end vehicle that is ready for any adventure you have in mind.

The exterior of this RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV is truly eye-catching with its premium Copper Crest paint and sporty F SPORT styling. It features triple-beam LED headlamps that light up the road beautifully and a power moonroof to enjoy the view above. The added running boards and 21 inch matte black wheels give this RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV a rugged yet sophisticated look. Plus, the power liftgate with a kick sensor makes loading your gear easier than ever.

Inside, you will find a cabin filled with luxury and clever tech. This RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV comes with leather and ultra-suede seats that are both heated and ventilated in the front and the back. The driver's cockpit includes a Heads-Up Display so you can keep your eyes on the road while seeing important info. With the 120V power outlet and a dedicated rear seat air conditioner, every passenger in this RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV will feel like they are traveling in first class.

The technology in this RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV is designed to make your life simpler. It features a massive Lexus Interface with built-in navigation and wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. For those who love music, the Mark Levinson audio system provides an incredible listening experience throughout the RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV. Safety is also a top priority with features like Lane Change Assist and a Surround View Camera to help you stay aware of everything around you.

Performance is where this RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV really shines. The adaptive suspension and auto-leveling system ensure the ride stays comfortable even on bumpy roads. You also get advanced safety systems that help with steering and braking to keep you on the right path. This RX 500h F SPORT Performance SUV is more than just a family car, it is a high-performance machine that makes every trip feel special.

2024 MAZDA MX-5 MIATA RF CLUB 2.0L — ONLINE DESCRIPTION

The 2024 Mazda MX-5 Miata RF Club 2.0L delivers pure driving excitement with precision engineering, lightweight performance, and iconic retractable fastback styling. Designed for enthusiasts who crave connection to the road, the Miata RF Club blends track-inspired performance with everyday usability and unmistakable style.

Performance & Driving Dynamics

2.0L SKYACTIV-G 4-Cylinder Engine

Approx. 181 horsepower with high-revving performance

Rear-Wheel Drive (RWD) for balanced, engaging handling

Lightweight chassis engineered for agility and responsiveness

Precise steering and exceptional road feedback

RF Club Trim Highlights

Power retractable hardtop fastback (RF) design

Sport-focused Club trim with performance upgrades

Aggressive exterior styling with aerodynamic accents

Performance wheels and brakes

Driver-centric cockpit built for spirited driving

Premium materials with a clean, minimalist interior layout

Interior & Technology

Sport seating designed for support and comfort

Touchscreen infotainment system with smartphone integration

Push-button start and keyless entry

Driver-focused controls with excellent visibility

Compact yet thoughtfully designed interior for daily use or weekend drives

Why Choose the MX-5 Miata RF Club?

This Miata is built for drivers who value feel, balance, and performance over excess. The RF Club trim adds a bold look and track-inspired hardware while keeping the legendary Miata driving experience intact. It’s one of the most engaging sports cars you can drive — at any speed.

SOUTHERN HOSPITALITY BUYER’S PROGRAM

Lifetime Oil & Filter Changes

Lifetime VA State Inspections

Lifetime Loaner Car Program if we don’t fix it right the first time

Additional exclusive dealership benefits designed to lower long-term ownership costs

Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.

description: Get behind the wheel of the 2023 Ford Expedition Limited 4WD a full size SUV built for families, road trippers, and adventurers alike. With bold styling, abundant power, and smart technology, this Expedition blends rugged capability with refined comfort to make every drive memorable and exciting.Thrilling Performance AllWeather Capability Potent 3.5L EcoBoost twinturbo V6 delivers around 400hp and 480lbft of torque, powering you confidently down highways or backroads. 10speed SelectShift automatic delivers smooth, responsive performance, while fulltime 4WD helps you tackle rain, snow, and rugged terrain with assurance. Robust towing capability perfect for boats, trailers, and weekend gear (up to 6,000lbs on Limited specs).Spacious Premium Interior Seating for up to seven passengers with versatile seating layouts and abundant head and legroom. Elegant touches like leathertrimmed seats, dualzone climate control, and thoughtful storage make every journey comfortable. Triplezone automatic climate and secondrow heat/air vents keep everyone happy on long trips.Modern Tech That Keeps You Connected Large SYNC infotainment display with Apple CarPlay Android Auto keeps navigation, music, calls, and apps right where you want them. Available premium Bang Olufsen audio (on some packages) makes every soundtrack sound amazing.Safety Confidence Features Standard Ford CoPilot360 technology includes forward collision warning, automatic emergency braking, lanekeeping assist, and blindspot monitoring for peace of mind. Advanced driveraid options like 360degree camera views and adaptive cruise control can elevate confidence on busy highways.Bold Style Meets RealWorld CapabilityWith striking exterior design cues, chrome accents, 20 wheels, and a commanding presence on the road, this Expedition Limited doesnt just perform it makes a statement.2023 Ford Expedition Limited 4WD where premium comfort, rugged capability, and familyready versatility come together to make every adventure unforgettable!

  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera with washer - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. Even if there are sloppy conditions, the washer keeps the camera's view clean. Rear camera with washer is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe
Technology and Telematics
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

With only 18,350 miles, this Transit features low mileage for its model year and a CARFAX 1-Owner history, offering confidence and value for businesses and contractors seeking reliable transportation. Interior practicality includes spacious cargo capacity with a low roof design for easy loading and secure transport of tools, supplies, or equipment. Standard convenience features such as Hands Free Bluetooth and a Back-Up Camera enhance daily functionality, improving safety and connectivity on the road and at job sites. The comfortable driver ergonomics and user-friendly controls make long days behind the wheel less taxing. This Transit is competitively priced and advertised as the best price in the area, providing exceptional value compared to similar offerings. Located in Suffolk, VA, the vehicle is available now for inspection and test drive. Easily set your speed in this 2024 Ford Transit Van T-250 Low Roof Slide with a state of the art cruise control system. Increase or decrease velocity with the touch of a button. This 2024 Ford Transit Van T-250 Low Roof Slide can run on either gasoline or E85 fuel. The fog lights cut through the weather so you can see what's ahead.

* , 2004 Maserati Coupe Cambiocorsa

- Only 23590 Miles
- 4.2L V8
- Automatic Transmission
- Gold Exterior
- Black Interior

Experience the blend of Italian elegance and thrilling performance with this 2004 Maserati Coupe Cambiocorsa. With only 23590 miles on the odometer this exquisite vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a low-mileage example of Maserati's renowned craftsmanship. Under the hood lies a potent 4.2L V8 engine delivering an exhilarating driving experience that seamlessly combines power and sophistication. Paired with an automatic transmission the Cambiocorsa ensures a smooth and responsive drive whether you're navigating city streets or open highways. The exterior of this Maserati Coupe is finished in a luxurious gold exuding a sense of timeless opulence and style. The sleek lines and aerodynamic design are a testament to Maserati's commitment to both aesthetics and performance. The gold paintwork not only highlights the car's elegant contours but also adds a touch of exclusivity making this coupe a true head-turner. Complementing the stunning exterior is a set of finely crafted alloy wheels further enhancing the vehicle's poised and polished appearance. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a meticulously designed black interior that offers a perfect balance of comfort and sportiness. The cabin features high-quality materials and fine craftsmanship creating a luxurious environment for both driver and passengers. The black leather seats provide excellent support and comfort while the intuitive layout of the controls ensures that everything you need is within easy reach. Every detail of the interior reflects Maserati's dedication to creating an unparalleled driving experience. Under the surface the 4.2L V8 engine roars with a distinctive Maserati sound embodying the spirit of Italian performance engineering. The automatic transmission allows for seamless gear changes providing both ease of use and the option for more spirited driving when desired. This Maserati Coupe is not just about luxury, it's a true performance machine capable of delivering thrilling acceleration and handling precision that will delight any driving enthusiast. In summary this 2004 Maserati Coupe Cambiocorsa is a stunning example of Italian automotive excellence. With its low mileage powerful V8 engine and luxurious gold exterior it represents a unique opportunity to own a piece of Maserati's storied heritage. The black interior offers a refined and comfortable space making every drive a pleasure. Don't miss the chance to experience the perfect blend of luxury and performance with this exceptional Maserati Coupe. Please call if interested or e-mail with specific questions. Thanks for looking!
