description:
Discover the ultimate blend of power, capability, and refined style in this 2023 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4 Turbo Diesel. This rugged yet sophisticated truck is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• Clean CARFAX/No Accidents
• Sport Step, Black (Dealer-Installed)
• AT4 Preferred Package
• Dynamic Blue Metallic Exterior

This Sierra 1500 AT4 is equipped with a powerful 3.0L Duramax Turbo Diesel I6 engine paired with a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission and capable 4-wheel drive system. Enjoy impressive fuel efficiency with an EPA-estimated 21 mpg in the city and 23 mpg on the highway.

The AT4 Preferred Package elevates your driving experience with a host of premium features, including:
• Universal Home Remote
• Rear Sliding Power Window
• Adaptive Cruise Control

Step into the spacious and well-appointed interior, where you'll find luxurious touches like heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a premium Bose sound system. Stay connected with the advanced GMC Infotainment System, featuring navigation, wireless charging, and seamless integration with your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto.

Designed to tackle any terrain, the Sierra 1500 AT4 boasts an off-road-tuned suspension, skid plates, and hill descent control to ensure you conquer the most challenging environments with confidence. The spray-on bedliner with the AT4 logo and integrated trailer brake controller make this truck a true workhorse, ready to handle all your hauling and towing needs.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like forward collision alert, lane keep assist, and rear cross-traffic braking keeping you and your loved ones secure on the road.

At our dealership, we are committed to delivering the highest quality and cleanliness with every used vehicle we sell. Each car undergoes an extensive reconditioning process to ensure it meets our rigorous standards. Beyond cleaning, our certified technicians conduct a thorough inspection and service, addressing routine maintenance such as oil changes, brake checks, tire rotations, and any necessary repairs to ensure optimal performance. This comprehensive approach ensures that every customer drives off with a vehicle that looks impeccable, runs smoothly, and offers the safety and reliability they deserve.

Dominate the trails and the commute in this 2024 Jeep Wrangler Sahara 4xe, finished in a commanding Black Clearcoat. description:
This Chevrolet Express with 69,587 miles is Car Bravo Certified, offering dependable performance and added peace of mind for buyers who need a vehicle thats built to work. Known for its durability and simple, proven design, the Express is a trusted choice for businesses, trades, and anyone needing a reliable cargo or work van solution.

Under the hood, the Express is engineered for long-term reliability and consistent performance. Its body-on-frame construction and robust drivetrain make it well-suited for hauling equipment, tools, or supplies day in and day out, whether around town or on longer highway runs.

Performance & Capability Highlights

Strong and proven engine designed for commercial use

Smooth automatic transmission

Rear-wheel drive for confident load handling

Heavy-duty suspension built for payload capability

4-wheel disc brakes with ABS for controlled stopping

Safety features are straightforward and effective, focusing on stability and protection while on the job:

Stability Control & Traction Control

Tire Pressure Monitoring System

Full airbag system

Daytime Running Lights

Inside, the Express keeps things practical and functional:

Durable seating surfaces built for daily use

Simple, easy-to-use controls

Ample cargo space ready for shelving or upfitting

Air conditioning for driver comfort

Power features for convenience (equipment dependent)

Technology & Convenience

AM/FM audio system with auxiliary input

Backup camera (where equipped)

Power windows and door locks (where equipped)

Multiple storage areas for work essentials

As a Car Bravo Certified vehicle, this Express has passed a thorough multi-point inspection and includes a 12-month/12,000-mile limited warranty, along with roadside assistancegiving you extra confidence and protection beyond the sale.

If youre looking for a reliable, work-ready van with certification-backed peace of mind, this Chevrolet Express is a smart, dependable choice ready to get the job done.

2016 Ford Transit-150 XLT 8-Passenger Van Only 13,017 Miles!

Available Now at Monadnock Ford 1147 Putney Road, Brattleboro, Vermont

Looking for a clean, low-mileage passenger van that's built for comfort, space, and Ford reliability? This White 2016 Ford Transit-150 XLT is the perfect fit for families, shuttle services, businesses, or anyone who needs reliable group transportation.

Whether you're driving through the hills of southern Vermont, running a shuttle in Keene, NH, or transporting a team through western Massachusetts, this Transit-150 delivers smooth performance, incredible space, and legendary Ford durability.

Vehicle Highlights & Performance

3.7L V6 Ti-VCT 24V Engine Proven reliability and strong power for passengers or cargo.

6-Speed Automatic Transmission with Overdrive Smooth shifting and long-lasting performance.

Rear-Wheel Drive (RWD) Excellent stability and road feel.

Seats up to 8 passengers comfortably with flexible layout options.

Exterior Upgrade Package Modern design with chrome accents.

Driver-Controlled Front & Rear Auxiliary A/C & Heater Ideal for passenger comfort.

Cruise Control with Message Center Easy long-distance driving.

ABS Brakes & Electronic Stability Control Safety and precision on every drive.

Traction Control & Low Tire Pressure Warning.

Remote Keyless Entry & Illuminated Entry.

Vinyl Sun Visors for added convenience.

The Ford Transit-150 XLT is known for its exceptional build quality and dependability. Its a favorite among Vermont businesses, airport shuttles, and large families who need a comfortable, spacious ride that performs well year after year.

Awards & Recognition

2016 KBB.com Brand Image Awards Recognized for outstanding design, dependability, and resale value.

This Transit isnt just a vanits a long-term investment in comfort, versatility, and reliability.

Built for Life in New England

From Brattleboros winding rural roads to the city streets of Keene and the snowy backroads of Hinsdale, the Transit-150 XLT is engineered to perform in all conditions. Its robust V6 engine and heavy-duty chassis handle Vermont winters with ease, while the advanced safety systems help keep you confident on every trip.

With 8-passenger capacity, this van is perfect for:

Large families or group travel.

Airport or hotel shuttle businesses.

Church, school, or community transportation.

Outdoor guides, tour companies, or local contractors.

Need to move people or gear efficiently? The Transit-150 does it allwith style and reliability only Ford can deliver.

Exceptional Value & Easy Financing

Priced below KBB Fair Purchase Price, this low-mileage van offers unbeatable value for both personal and commercial use. At Monadnock Ford, we make it easy to get behind the wheel with flexible financing, fair trade-in appraisals, and a transparent buying processno surprises, no pressure, just great deals on great vehicles.

You can even start your purchase online for a fast and convenient experience.

Service, Support & Trust

As part of the Maverick Motor Group, Monadnock Ford gives you access to over 400 quality new, used, and certified vehicles daily. Our Quick Lane Service Center provides fast, no-appointment maintenance, oil changes, and tire carekeeping your Transit on the road where it belongs.

We proudly serve customers from Brattleboro, VT, Keene, NH, Hinsdale, NH, Bellows Falls, VT, Greenfield, MA, and beyond.

description:
Discover the epitome of modern automotive engineering with the 2024 Toyota Venza Limited. This sophisticated crossover SUV seamlessly blends style, performance, and advanced technology, making it the perfect companion for your family's adventures.

Indulge in the exceptional features that set this Venza apart:

• Android Auto
• Apple CarPlay
• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth
• Carfax 1-Owner
• Leather Seats
• Navigation

Elevate your driving experience with the Venza's powerful yet efficient 2.5L 4-cylinder engine, delivering an impressive 40 city/37 highway MPG. The standard All-Wheel Drive system ensures confident handling in any condition, while the Continuously Variable Transmission (ECVT) provides a smooth, responsive ride.

This Toyota Venza Limited is more than just a remarkable vehicle – it's a testament to the brand's commitment to quality and innovation. As a Toyota Certified Pre-Owned model, it has undergone a rigorous inspection and comes with the reassurance of a comprehensive warranty, giving you the peace of mind you deserve.

Imagine yourself behind the wheel, surrounded by the Venza's luxurious interior. Sink into the comfortable, ventilated leather seats and enjoy the convenience of the Head-Up Display, Hands-Free Power Liftgate, and the premium JBL audio system. The Venza's advanced safety features, including Automatic High Beams, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, provide an extra layer of protection for you and your loved ones.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or navigating the daily commute, the 2024 Toyota Venza Limited is the perfect companion. Its spacious cabin, versatile cargo area, and cutting-edge technology make it the ultimate crossover SUV. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Venza's exceptional blend of style, performance, and value.

In conclusion, the 2024 Toyota Venza Limited is a remarkable vehicle that combines the best of Toyota's engineering prowess with the latest advancements in automotive technology. Visit our showroom today and discover why this Venza is the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

description: . Sporty and functional, our 2024 Toyota Sienna XSE AWD Minivan can quickly become your family's favorite ride in Ruby Flare Pearl! Powered by a 2.5 Liter 4 Cylinder and 2 Electric Motors supplying a combined 245hp to an eCVT. This All Wheel Drive minivan shows its athletic side with sport-tuned suspension and steering systems, and it achieves nearly 36mpg on the highway. Our Sienna sets you up in grand style thanks to LED lighting, wide-angle fog lamps, bold black rocker panels, matching mirror caps, an aggressive black metallic grille, 20-inch dark alloy wheels, a sunroof, hands-free power-sliding side doors, and a power liftgate. Our XSE cabin comfortably fits up to seven with heated SofTex® power front sport seats, second-row captain's chairs, a Split & Stow third row, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, four-zone automatic climate control, and keyless entry/ignition. 2024 Toyota Sienna Hybrid LE — Wheelchair Accessible Van |43,086 Miles | Grace Auto Group
----------
- Uber & Lyft drivers – Approved for rideshare wheelchair transport.
- Taxi operators – Meets TLC and Yellow Cab requirements.
- Families caring for a wheelchair-bound loved one – Safe, affordable, and easy to operate.
- NEMT companies – Dependable vans built for continuous medical transportation use.
----------
Key Features & Mobility Conversion Highlights
Hybrid Efficiency & Powertrain
- 2.5L Hybrid Synergy Drive® engine with Electronic CVT for seamless power delivery
- Impressive fuel efficiency ideal for both personal and professional use
- Whisper-quiet operation enhances comfort for wheelchair passengers
Mobility Conversion & Accessibility
- Professionally installed AMT Advanced Mobility Solutions rear-entry wheelchair conversion
- Low-angle, easy-to-deploy ramp with a lowered floor for smooth entry and exit
- ADA-compliant design with secure wheelchair tie-downs and restraint system
- Spacious, open interior layout for comfortable wheelchair maneuverability
- Retains key factory features while enhancing accessibility and convenience
Interior Comfort & Technology
- Premium cloth seating with power-adjustable driver’s seat
- Tri-zone automatic climate control for passenger comfort
- 9-inch touchscreen infotainment with Apple CarPlay® & Android Auto™
- Bluetooth® hands-free calling and media streaming
- USB ports, auxiliary inputs, and rearview camera
Safety & Driver Assistance
- Toyota Safety Sense™ 2.0: Pre-Collision System, Lane Departure Alert, and Dynamic Radar Cruise Control
- Blind Spot Monitor and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert
- Stability and traction control for confident driving
- Multiple airbags and advanced braking systems
Exterior & Convenience
- Power sliding side doors and power liftgate for easy access
- Alloy wheels and sleek, modern design
- Clean, professional look perfect for personal or commercial use
-----------
Why Choose Grace Auto Group for Your Wheelchair Accessible Van
At Grace Auto Group, we’re proud to be an Authorized AMT Advanced Mobility Solutions Dealer, providing top-tier mobility options for individuals and organizations throughout Pennsylvania and beyond.
Our Mobility Program Includes:
- Authorized AMT Advanced Mobility Solutions Dealer
- Wide selection of rear-entry Toyota, Chrysler, and Honda vans
- TLC, Yellow Cab & ADA-approved conversions
- Convert your own van with AMT rear-entry solutions
- Flexible financing options for families and businesses
- Expert service & support before and after your purchase
- Warranty on every vehicle and conversion

    Convenience
    • This \'intelligent\' cruise control system uses laser or radar to maintain a preset following distance behind another vehicle, automatically braking (to a complete stop if needed) or accelerating as required.
    Safety and Security
    • With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.
    • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
    • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
    • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
    • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display. The camera is equipped with its own washer.
    • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display. The camera is equipped with its own washer.
    • A head-up display projects gauge (speed, RPM, etc.) information onto the inside of the windshield just below the driver's line of sight.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.
    • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

description:
Thank you for stopping by our virtual showroom! This 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Pinnacle offered in Silver Mist Clearcoat will make a great addition to your family or business! Be sure to take note of all this vehicle has to offer: Packages & Features Quick Order Package 27S
    Comfort
    • Ventilated front seats -That's cool. Ventilated front seats provides targeted cool air so you and your passenger can get comfortable quicker in hot weather. Getting comfortable is no sweat when you have ventilated front seats.
    Convenience
    • Smart device and keyfob engine start control - Phone ahead. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob or your smart device, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, ,thanks to Smart device and Keyfob engine start control.
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    In-car Entertainment
    • Entertainment system with Blu-ray and digital media - Keep boredom at bay. Whether it's driving cross- country or making a quick trip around town, your passengers' favorite videos can come, too! description: The 2025 Honda Odyssey EX-L is a remarkable family-focused vehicle that combines exceptional versatility, advanced technology, and refined style. With its striking Smoke Blue Pearl exterior and a host of premium features, this Odyssey is poised to exceed your expectations.Meticulously equipped, this Odyssey EX-L boasts an impressive array of must-have amenities, including:• Backup Camera• Bluetooth Hands-Free Calling• Built-in USB Ports• Remote Engine Start• Leather Seats• Heated Seats• Around View Monitor Advanced Technology• Sunroof/Moonroof• Push Button Start• XM Satellite Radio• Apple CarPlay• Android AutoUnder the hood, the Odyssey's powerful 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 10-Speed Automatic transmission, delivers an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/28 highway mpg.Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin that showcases Honda's commitment to quality and attention to detail. The Odyssey's leather-trimmed seats, heated front buckets, and power driver's seat provide unparalleled comfort, while the split-folding third-row seat and ample cargo space ensure versatility for all your family's needs.The advanced technology features in this Odyssey EX-L are designed to keep you connected and in control. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, the clarity of the 160-Watt AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM audio system, and the added peace of mind from the Blind Spot Information (BSI) System and Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS).Safety is also a top priority, with the Odyssey EX-L boasting a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Collision Mitigation Braking System, and more.Whether you're embarking on family road trips, shuttling the kids to activities, or simply enjoying your daily commute, the 2025 Honda Odyssey EX-L is poised to be your trusted companion, offering unparalleled versatility, technology, and refinement. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology in the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited. This exceptional minivan is a true masterpiece, designed to elevate your driving experience and cater to your every need.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, the Pacifica Limited is a testament to Chrysler's commitment to innovation. Indulge in the convenience of the Navigation System, the immersive sound of the 13 Speakers, and the seamless integration of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. Experience the ultimate in climate control with the Dual Zone Automatic Temperature Control and the Rear Air Conditioning, ensuring everyone on board enjoys a comfortable ride.

• Navigation System
• 13 Speakers
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Dual Zone Automatic Temperature Control
• Rear Air Conditioning
• Power Liftgate
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Nappa Leather Seats
• Ventilated Front Seats
• Heated Front and Rear Seats
• Power Adjustable Driver's Seat
• Power Adjustable Passenger Seat
• Panoramic Sunroof
• Rear-View Camera
• Blind Spot Monitoring
• Adaptive Cruise Control

Step inside the Pacifica Limited and be captivated by the refined Nappa Leather Bucket Seats with the S Logo, offering unparalleled comfort and style. Enjoy the convenience of the Power Liftgate, the Heated Steering Wheel, and the Ventilated Front Seats, ensuring you and your passengers travel in the utmost comfort.

The Pacifica's performance is equally impressive, with a powerful 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and a 9-Speed 948TE Automatic Transmission providing a smooth and efficient ride. With an EPA-estimated 19 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, this minivan delivers exceptional fuel efficiency, making it an ideal choice for your daily commute or family adventures.

Safety is paramount in the Pacifica Limited, with a comprehensive suite of advanced features, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear-View Camera, and Adaptive Cruise Control, ensuring you and your loved ones arrive at your destination with confidence and peace of mind.

Discover the perfect balance of style, technology, and functionality in the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional minivan.

Experience the pinnacle of family-friendly luxury with the 2025 Toyota Sienna LE 8 Passenger. This exceptional minivan combines cutting-edge technology, unparalleled comfort, and exceptional efficiency to elevate your daily driving.

• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio data system
• Radio: Toyota Audio Multimedia

• Rear air conditioning

• Remote keyless entry

Powered by a 2.5L I4 Hybrid engine with VVT-iE DOHC 16V and CVT, the Sienna LE delivers an impressive 36 MPG in both city and highway driving, ensuring exceptional fuel efficiency and a reduced environmental impact. Its spacious interior, with seating for up to 8 passengers, offers ample room for the entire family and their cargo.

Elevate your driving experience with the Sienna's comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Lane Departure Warning System, Exterior Parking Camera Rear, and an Emergency communication system. These cutting-edge technologies work tirelessly to help keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Indulge in the convenience of the Sienna's premium amenities, such as Automatic temperature control, Front dual zone A/C, and Remote keyless entry. These features seamlessly integrate to create a sanctuary of comfort and convenience, making every journey a pleasure.

With its striking Red exterior and impeccable craftsmanship, the 2025 Toyota Sienna LE 8 Passenger exudes a sense of sophistication and style that is sure to turn heads. Discover the perfect balance of form and function with this exceptional minivan.

Experience the ultimate in family-focused driving with the 2025 Toyota Sienna LE 8 Passenger. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your daily life. We're confident you'll be impressed by its unparalleled capabilities and eager to make it your own.

description:
Discover the epitome of modern family luxury with the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited. This exceptional minivan seamlessly blends style, technology, and unparalleled comfort, making it the ultimate choice for the discerning driver.

Adorned in a stunning Ceramic Gray Clearcoat exterior, the Pacifica Limited exudes a refined and sophisticated presence. Boasting a wealth of premium features, this vehicle is tailored to elevate your driving experience. Key highlights include:

• Nappa Leather Bucket Seats with S Logo
• Power Moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• 20" x 7.5" S-Model Aluminum Design 1 Wheels
• Integrated Active Noise Cancellation
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and equipped with a 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, the Pacifica Limited delivers an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency, achieving an impressive 19 city and 28 highway MPG.

Step inside and be captivated by the Pacifica's spacious and meticulously crafted cabin. The Nappa Leather Bucket Seats with S Logo provide unparalleled comfort, while the heated front and rear seats, as well as the ventilated front seats, ensure year-round comfort. The Uconnect 5 Nav system with a 10.1" display seamlessly integrates your digital world, offering navigation, entertainment, and advanced connectivity.

Designed with your family's safety in mind, the Pacifica Limited is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, Occupant Sensing Airbag, and Electronic Stability Control. The ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera and Blind Spot Monitoring system further enhance your confidence behind the wheel.

With a Clean Carfax and just one previous owner, this 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited represents an exceptional value. Priced at $33,795, it is a true standout in its class, offering unmatched quality, features, and peace of mind.

Experience the pinnacle of family transportation by scheduling a test drive today. We are confident that the Pacifica Limited will exceed your expectations and become the perfect companion for all your adventures.

Thank you for choosing Basil Toyota, this Bright White Clearcoat 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Select is a great choice! Check out the following: One Owner! No Accidents! City 19/Hwy 28 Quick Order Package 27L
    ENGINE: 3.6L V6 24V VVT UPG I W/ESS, TRANSMISSION: 9-SPEED 948TE AUTOMATIC, QUICK ORDER PACKAGE 27L, WHEELS: 17\' X 7.0\' ALUMINUM, TIRES: 235/65R17 BSW AS, BRIGHT WHITE CLEARCOAT, BLACK, CAPRICE LEATHERETTE BUCKET SEATS, MANUFACTURER'S STATEMENT OF ORIGIN, BLACK SEATS, SIRIUSXM GUARDIAN - INCLUDED TRIAL (B) Comfort
    • Heated steering wheel - A warm touch. Trying to drive with bulky winter gloves on isn't always easy. Keep your hands warm in cold temperatures so you can ditch the mitts and get a firm grip with this heated steering wheel.
    Convenience
    • Smart device and keyfob engine start control - Phone ahead. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob or your smart device, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, ,thanks to Smart device and Keyfob engine start control.
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
    Safety and Security
    • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. Blind spot warning alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear so you know if you're about to make an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with confidence and safety with blind spot warning.

Discover the Pinnacle of Comfort and Convenience in the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited. This exceptional minivan is a true masterpiece, designed to elevate your driving experience and exceed your every expectation.

Boasting a stunning Gray exterior, this Pacifica Limited is more than just a vehicle – it's a statement of refined style and uncompromising quality. Equipped with a powerful 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and a smooth 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, this minivan delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 19 city/28 highway MPG.

• Quick Order Package 27P
• Ceramic Gray Clearcoat
• Gray

But the true allure of this Pacifica lies in its unparalleled features and amenities. Indulge in the convenience of the Navigation System, the immersive audio experience of the 13 Speakers, and the seamless connectivity of the Uconnect 5 Nav with 10.1" Display. Stay comfortable in all seasons with the Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control, Heated Front Seats, and Heated Rear Seats.

Elevate your driving experience with the Power Liftgate, Power Moonroof, and Hands-Free Sliding Doors, allowing you to effortlessly load and unload with ease. Enjoy the added security of the Chrysler Connect Emergency Communication System and the peace of mind provided by the comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Automatic Emergency Braking.

Designed with your family's well-being in mind, the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited offers uncompromising versatility and comfort. With seating for up to eight and a wealth of cargo space, this minivan is the perfect companion for your adventures, whether it's a road trip with loved ones or a weekend getaway.

Why Buy from Paragon Honda? When you choose this 2025 Honda Odyssey EX-L from Paragon Honda, you're not just buying a used car - you're investing in quality, reliability, and peace of mind. Located in Woodside, NY 11377, we're proud to offer the best selection of certified pre-owned Hondavehicles and top-tier used cars in the Queens area. Here's why savvy buyers trust us: Transparent Pricing: At $$36,700, what you see is what you pay. Certified Quality: Every vehicle, like this 2025 Honda Odyssey EX-L, undergoes a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our high standards. Unmatched Warranty: Vehicles less than 6 years old and less than 80,000 miles get a:
  • 7yr/100k Powertrain limited warranty from original in-service date
  • + 24 months/80,000 miles limited Non- Powertrain warranty.
  • Two complimentary oil changes will be offered.
  • XM 3 months free trial period.
  • Trip interruption. Customer-First Service: Our award-winning team treats you like family, backed by an excellent customer satisfaction rating. Convenience: From complimentary pick-up and delivery for service and sales, to easy financing options, we make car buying stress-free. Also for your convenience: we have our service department open 24 hours a day and 7 days a week. No Accidents! One Owner! CRYSTAL BLACK PEARL, BLACK, LEATHER TRIMMED SEATS Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
    Ready to drive home this 2025 Honda Odyssey EX-L today at Paragon Honda in Queens NY or Call us at 718-550-1710 to schedule your visit. Don't miss out - at this price $$36,700 it won't last long! description:
2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited – The Ultimate Family Commuter
Take your family travels to the next level with this CARFAX One-Owner 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited. Dressed in a sophisticated Diamond Black Crystal Pearlcoat, this luxury passenger van combines the trusted performance of a 3.6L V6 engine with the sleek, aggressive styling of the S Appearance Package. From daily school drop-offs in Lowell to weekend road trips across the Midwest, the Pacifica is engineered to make every mile feel like a first-class experience.

Premium Interior & Versatile Comfort
The cabin of the Limited trim is designed with every passenger in mind. Experience the luxury of Heated and Ventilated Nappa Leather front seats, while your second-row passengers enjoy Heated Captain’s Chairs. The Stow 'n Go® seating system remains the industry gold standard, allowing you to fold the second and third rows flat into the floor for a massive 140.5 cubic feet of cargo space in seconds.

High-Tech Connectivity & Entertainment
Stay connected and entertained with the Uconnect 5 Nav system featuring a massive 10.1-inch touchscreen display. With wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, your favorite apps and navigation are always at your fingertips. This Pacifica also features the Quick Order Package 27P, ensuring you have the latest in tech, including a Wi-Fi Hotspot and a premium audio system to keep the whole crew happy.

Safety You Can Trust
Your family’s safety is a top priority, and the 2025 Pacifica is loaded with driver-assistance technology. Navigate tight spots with ease using the ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera and stay centered on the road with Lane Departure Warning. Additional peace of mind comes from the Blind Spot Monitor and Forward Collision Warning, making this one of the safest vehicles on the road today.

Key Features & Highlights:
Performance: 3.6L V6 Engine, 9-Speed Automatic Transmission, FWD.

Exterior: 20-inch S-Model Aluminum Wheels, Power Sunroof, LED Fog Lamps.

Interior: 7-Passenger 3rd Row Seating, Heated Steering Wheel, Dual-Zone Climate Control.

Convenience: Remote Start, Power Liftgate, Hands-Free Bluetooth.

Efficiency: EPA-estimated 19/28 City/Highway MPG.

Stay connected with integrated navigation, wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot, and 11 USB ports to keep everyone charged. The power liftgate and adaptive cruise control with stop-and-go make every journey effortless.

This beautiful vehicle was recently acquired to our store here in St. Louis!

This CARFAX One-Owner vehicle was well maintained and serviced on time.

The Toyota Sienna XLE Hybrid focuses on space, comfort, and family utility. The Gray SofTex interior and 8-passenger seating layout make daily driving, road trips, and family hauling simple and practical.

Key Features

- 2.5L Hybrid powertrain producing 245 net combined horsepower paired with an Electronic CVT

- Front-Wheel Drive for confident everyday driving

- 8-passenger seating with second-row bench and split-and-stow third-row seat

- Hands-free dual power sliding doors and power liftgate

- Flexible cargo area with flat load floor and multiple storage solutions

- 12.3-inch Toyota Audio Multimedia touchscreen with wireless Apple CarPlay & Android Auto and 6 USB charge ports

- Four-zone automatic climate control, heated and power-adjustable front seats

- Toyota Safety Sense with adaptive cruise control, lane departure alert, blind spot monitoring, rear cross-traffic alert, and parking assist with automatic braking

- Power tilt-and-slide moonroof and factory roof rails

We just completed our Victory 182-point inspection, performed a maintenance inspection and battery test, topped off all fluids, and completed a full interior and exterior detail. Two keys included.

Recent service records show routine maintenance completed and vehicle fully reconditioned to Victory standards.

This beauty has had and passed an extensive Victory 182-point inspection conducted by our factory-certified technicians.

Buy with confidence. Every Victory Pre-Owned vehicle includes a 90-day or 3,000-mile comprehensive warranty, on top of any remaining factory coverage. Also included is Car Doc Smart Connect, allowing you to monitor fuel level, battery status, vehicle location, recalls, and maintenance scheduling right from your phone.

Ownership includes our Car Doc Maintenance Plan with 6 complimentary oil changes and 6 complimentary tire rotations during the first two years. Upgrade options are available for 3-year or 5-year Car Doc plans for added perks.

We are in the business of building relationships, not just selling vehicles.

Whether you have good credit, bad credit, or no credit, get pre-approved today:
https://www.victorytoyotastl.com/finance/get-pre-approved/

This vehicle WONT last long at this price! We are a large used-car superstore proudly serving St. Louis, Kirkwood, Chesterfield, Ballwin, Fenton, and surrounding Missouri communities.

Do not waste any time call us now at (314) 966-5404.

Please chat, email, text, or call to verify any information and schedule your product preview.

Pricamo Bosanski/Hablamos Espanol

Power and efficiency: Efficient yet capable powertrain provides smooth acceleration and composed highway cruising while maintaining competitive fuel economy for a vehicle of its size. Exterior and utility: Bold exterior styling, premium alloy wheels, and LED lighting give the Carnival a modern presence. Sliding rear doors and low step in height simplify passenger access. Intuitive infotainment with touchscreen, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto enhances connectivity and entertainment on the go.

Safety and driver assistance: Advanced driver assistance features provide layered protection, including forward collision mitigation, lane keeping assist, blind spot monitoring, and adaptive cruise control for confident highway driving. Solid construction and modern safety systems increase occupant protection and peace of mind.

Condition and value: Clean Carfax history, minimal dealer preparation, and full service inspection make this Carnival EX a compelling value for buyers seeking nearly new condition without the new vehicle price. description:
Elevate Your Driving Experience with the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited

Discover the epitome of family-friendly luxury with the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited. This stunning minivan offers an unparalleled blend of style, comfort, and advanced technology, making it the ultimate choice for discerning drivers.

• Ceramic Gray Clearcoat exterior
• Gray interior
• Navigation System
• Quick Order Package 27P
• 13 Speakers
• Integrated Active Noise Cancellation
• Uconnect 5 Nav with 10.1" Display
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Power Liftgate
• Panoramic Sunroof
• ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Nappa Leather Bucket Seats with S Logo
• Ventilated Front Seats

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, the Pacifica Limited delivers an exceptional driving experience. With an impressive fuel efficiency of 19 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, this minivan strikes the perfect balance between power and efficiency.

Step inside and be captivated by the Pacifica Limited's luxurious interior. The Nappa Leather Bucket Seats with S Logo provide unparalleled comfort, while the heated and ventilated front seats ensure you and your passengers stay cozy in any weather. The expansive panoramic sunroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere.

Cutting-edge technology is at your fingertips with the Uconnect 5 Nav system, featuring a stunning 10.1-inch display. Seamlessly integrate your smartphone via Apple CarPlay or Android Auto, and enjoy your favorite music, podcasts, and navigation with ease.

For added peace of mind, the Pacifica Limited is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including the ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Adaptive Cruise Control. These innovative technologies work together to help keep you and your loved ones protected on the road.

Experience the epitome of family-focused luxury with the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited. Elevate your driving experience and discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology that will exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Pacifica Limited is the ultimate choice for your next vehicle.

Introducing the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited, a versatile and sophisticated family-friendly vehicle that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and cutting-edge technology. This one-owner gem is the perfect companion for your daily adventures and weekend getaways, offering an unparalleled driving experience.

Boasting a sleek black exterior and a meticulously maintained interior, this Pacifica Limited is a true head-turner. Equipped with a powerful 3.6L V6 engine and a 9-speed automatic transmission, it delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 19 city and 28 highway MPG.

Elevate your driving experience with a host of premium features:

• Google Android Auto™ and Apple CarPlay®
• Bluetooth® hands-free connectivity
• Navigation system
• Premium audio system with 13 speakers
• Multi-zone climate controls
• Heated and ventilated front seats
• Heated second-row seats
• Power sliding doors
• Leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob
• Power liftgate
• Backup camera
• Cruise control

This Pacifica Limited also offers advanced safety features, including a suite of airbags, electronic stability control, and the ParkView® Rear Back-Up Camera, ensuring your peace of mind on the road.

Indulge in the ultimate in comfort and convenience with the Pacifica Limited's spacious and versatile interior. The split-folding third-row seats and power-adjustable driver's seat with memory function allow you to tailor the cabin to your needs, while the Nappa leather-trimmed seats and heated steering wheel add a touch of luxury.

Whether you're transporting the family, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, the 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Limited is the perfect companion. Its exceptional capabilities, refined styling, and cutting-edge technology make it a standout in the minivan segment. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

If you’re shopping for a nearly new hybrid minivan with luxury features and real fuel efficiency, this 2025 Kia Carnival Hybrid SX checks every box. With just over 7,000 miles and priced well below original MSRP, it delivers huge value for families who want space, technology, and lower fuel costs without paying full new-car pricing.

This Carnival is a CARFAX One Owner and Kia Certified Pre-Owned, meaning it’s been through a full 165-point inspection and comes with factory-backed warranty coverage. Original MSRP was over $53K, and this one lands in a far more comfortable price range with the heavy depreciation already behind it.

The Hybrid SX trim is fully loaded. You’ll find heated and ventilated front seats, memory seating, navigation, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, power liftgate, rain-sensing wipers, and a smooth, quiet hybrid powertrain delivering up to 34 MPG city. The dual-screen rear seat entertainment system and power second-row moonroof make this an easy win for families with kids or anyone who spends time on the road.

The Carnival continues to be one of the most comfortable and versatile family vehicles available. If you’re cross-shopping a Toyota Sienna Hybrid, Honda Odyssey, or Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid, the Carnival stands out for interior design, technology, and long-term warranty coverage.

As a Kia Certified vehicle, this Carnival includes a 10-year or 100,000-mile powertrain limited warranty from the original in-service date, 12-month or 12,000-mile Platinum coverage, roadside assistance, rental car reimbursement, transferable warranty, and a low deductible. That’s thousands in coverage included at no extra cost.

  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

This 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Select is an exceptional family-friendly minivan that offers unparalleled versatility, comfort, and advanced technology. With its sleek black exterior and meticulously maintained interior, this Pacifica is a true head-turner that will make you the envy of the neighborhood.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine mated to a smooth-shifting 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, delivering an impressive balance of performance and efficiency with 19 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway. The Pacifica's front-wheel-drive system provides confident handling and a comfortable ride, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or family adventures.

Step inside this well-equipped Pacifica and you'll be greeted by a wealth of premium features, including a stunning 10.1" Touchscreen Display, Apple CarPlay, and SiriusXM Guardian connectivity. The Caprice Leatherette Bucket Seats offer exceptional comfort and support, while the 360 Surround View Camera System and Parallel and Perpendicular Park Assist with Stop make navigating tight spaces a breeze.

Safety is also a top priority in the Pacifica, with advanced features like Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, and Electronic Stability Control ensuring your peace of mind on the road. The Power Liftgate and 3rd Row Seating further enhance the Pacifica's versatility, making it the ideal choice for families on the go.

description:
Discover the ultimate family-friendly ride with the 2025 Toyota Sienna LE 8 Passenger. This exceptional minivan combines style, comfort, and cutting-edge technology to elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures.

Boasting a stunning Gray exterior, this Sienna LE is equipped with an impressive array of features:

• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth, Hands-Free
• Radio: Toyota Audio Multimedia
• Automatic temperature control
• Power driver seat
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Illuminated entry
• 3rd row seats: split-bench
• Alloy wheels

Beneath the sleek exterior lies the powerful yet efficient 2.5L I4 Hybrid engine with VVT-iE DOHC 16V, delivering an impressive 34 city MPG and 36 highway MPG. The seamless CVT and standard AWD system ensure a smooth, confident ride in any condition.

Step inside and experience the unparalleled comfort and convenience of the Sienna LE. The spacious interior features seating for up to 8 passengers, allowing you to easily accommodate your growing family or transport friends and gear with ease. The split-folding third-row seat and ample cargo space provide the flexibility to adapt to your ever-changing needs.

Cutting-edge technology takes center stage, with features like the Toyota Audio Multimedia system, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration, keeping you connected and entertained on the go. The Backup Camera and Exterior Parking Camera Rear enhance visibility and safety, while the Automatic temperature control and Illuminated entry add to the overall refinement.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the Sienna LE delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features, including Lane Departure Warning System, Auto High-beam Headlights, and Electronic Stability Control, giving you and your loved ones the peace of mind you deserve.

Experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and practicality with the 2025 Toyota Sienna LE 8 Passenger. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional minivan can transform your daily driving and family adventures.

This 2025 Kia Carnival LXS is a versatile and well-equipped family vehicle that offers a wealth of advanced features and amenities. The Carnival's advanced technology includes a state-of-the-art navigation system, a premium audio system, and seamless smartphone integration through Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. Dual-zone climate control, heated front seats, and a reclining third-row seat ensure exceptional comfort for all passengers.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like automatic high-beam headlights, a rear-view camera, and a comprehensive suite of airbags and driver-assist technologies. The Carnival's independent suspension and responsive steering provide a smooth and confident driving experience, whether navigating city streets or tackling longer road trips.

As a Kia Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this Carnival has undergone a rigorous 165-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty and roadside assistance program. You can have peace of mind knowing that this minivan has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide years of reliable and enjoyable service.

Since 1975, we've been committed to providing a safe, transparent, and enjoyable car-buying experience. This 2025 Honda Odyssey EX-L is a standout in the minivan segment, offering a winning combination of style, comfort, and advanced technology. With its sleek exterior, spacious interior, and impressive performance, this Odyssey is the perfect companion for your growing family.

• BLUETOOTH HANDSFREE
• APPLE CARPLAY
• REAR VIEW CAMERA
• Blind Spot Monitor
• 7 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Automatic temperature control
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow
• 18" Machine-Finished Alloy Wheels

Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine delivers a smooth and efficient ride, with an impressive 19 city/28 highway MPG. The 10-Speed Automatic transmission ensures seamless power delivery, making this Odyssey a joy to drive, whether you're navigating city streets or hitting the open road.

This 2025 Honda Odyssey EX-L is a J.D. Power Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, which means it has been thoroughly inspected and comes with a 90-day or 3,000-mile Platinum Warranty. This gives you the peace of mind of owning a high-quality, well-maintained vehicle that you can trust.

With its spacious and versatile interior, the Odyssey offers ample room for your family and all their gear. The power liftgate and split-folding rear seats make loading and unloading a breeze, while the leather-trimmed seats and heated front seats provide exceptional comfort on every journey.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like the Blind Spot Information (BSI) System, Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS), and Adaptive Cruise Control keeping you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Don't miss your chance to experience the exceptional value and quality of this 2025 Honda Odyssey EX-L. Visit Marietta Toyota today and let us show you why this minivan is the perfect fit for your family.

description:
Experience the pinnacle of family-friendly luxury with the 2025 Toyota Sienna XLE 7 Passenger. This exceptional minivan seamlessly blends advanced technology, premium comfort, and exceptional versatility to elevate your daily drives.

Boasting a robust suite of features, this Sienna is tailored to your needs:

• BODY SIDE MOLDINGS (TMS)
• MUDGUARDS (TMS)
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Power Liftgate
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Garage door transmitter: HomeLink
• Front Heated Bucket Seats
• Power passenger seat
• Split folding rear seat
• 17" Alloy Wheels

Powered by a 2.5L I4 Hybrid engine with AWD, the Sienna delivers an impressive 34 city/36 highway MPG, making it both efficient and capable. Its spacious, well-appointed interior offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, with features like dual-zone climate control, a power driver's seat, and a panoramic moonroof.

Safety is paramount in the Sienna, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Lane Departure Warning, Auto High-Beam Headlights, and Brake Assist. You and your family can travel with confidence, knowing you're protected by Toyota's renowned safety engineering.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or navigating the daily school run, the 2025 Toyota Sienna XLE 7 Passenger is the ultimate companion. Experience the perfect balance of style, technology, and utility that will elevate your driving experience. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this remarkable minivan for a test drive. Let us demonstrate how the Sienna can transform your daily drives and family adventures.

OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: PLATINUM WHITE PEARL, BLACK, LEATHER TRIMMED SEATS Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2025 Toyota Sienna XLE, a modern marvel that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and cutting-edge technology. This captivating minivan is poised to elevate your driving experience, offering a refined and versatile solution for your family's needs.

Boasting a sleek Gray exterior, the Sienna XLE commands attention with its striking presence. Under the hood, the powerful 2.5L I4 Hybrid engine with VVT-iE DOHC 16V and CVT transmission delivers an impressive 36 MPG in the city and on the highway, making it an exceptional choice for your daily commute and weekend adventures.

• Power Liftgate
• Power Moonroof
• Heated Front Seats
• Lane Departure Warning System
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-Beam Headlights
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• 8-Speaker Audio System
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Keyless Entry with Remote Start
• 17-Inch Alloy Wheels
• Roof Rails

Step inside the Sienna XLE and experience the epitome of modern luxury. The spacious and well-appointed cabin offers seating for up to 8 passengers, with SofTex-trimmed seats and a power-adjustable driver's seat providing unparalleled comfort. The advanced infotainment system, complete with an 8-inch touchscreen display, seamlessly integrates your smartphone and delivers a premium audio experience.

Safety is paramount in the Sienna XLE, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including the Lane Departure Warning System, Automatic High Beams, and Rear Parking Camera, ensuring you and your loved ones are protected on every journey.

Whether you're transporting your growing family, embarking on a road trip, or simply seeking a versatile and efficient daily driver, the 2025 Toyota Sienna XLE is the perfect companion. Experience the exceptional craftsmanship, cutting-edge features, and uncompromising performance that make this minivan a true standout in its class.

We invite you to visit our showroom and take the Sienna XLE for a test drive. Discover the difference that this remarkable vehicle can make in your life. Let us help you find the perfect Sienna XLE to suit your unique needs and lifestyle.

description:
Recent Arrival!

The 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Select AWD is finished in Bright White Clear-Coat and blends modern minivan styling with added all-wheel-drive capability. Exterior features include bi-function LED projector headlamps, LED front fog lamps, LED tail lamps, automatic headlamps, power sliding doors, and a power liftgate, giving the Pacifica a clean, functional appearance designed for daily family use and seasonal driving conditions.

Inside, the cabin features Caprice leatherette bucket seats in a Black interior and is designed around flexibility and comfort. Interior highlights include second- and third-row Stow n Go seating with easy-tilt access, an 8-way power adjustable driver seat with memory, heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, second-row in-floor storage bins, a floor console with covered storage, three-zone automatic climate control, power front and rear windows with one-touch up and down, and a universal garage-door opener.

Technology is centered around Uconnect 5 with a 10.1-inch touchscreen display and includes Apple CarPlay, Google Android Auto, SiriusXM radio with three-month subscription, hands-free phone and audio, Chrysler Connect connected services with trial, and a 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot, keeping passengers connected and entertained across all rows.

Power comes from the 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine with Stop/Start paired to a 9-speed automatic transmission and an AWD suspension system. Safety and driver-assist features include adaptive cruise control with stop and go, blind-spot and rear cross-path detection, lane-departure warning plus, full-speed forward-collision warning plus, pedestrian emergency braking, advanced brake assist, ParkView rear back-up camera, ParkSense rear park-assist with stop, rear-seat reminder alert, advanced multistage airbags, side-curtain airbags for all rows, and front seat-mounted side airbags.

Added equipment includes Customer Preferred Package 27L, Safety Sphere with 360-degree surround-view camera system, front and rear ParkSense with parallel and perpendicular park assist, and a dual-pane panoramic sunroof with power open and close shade. These additions result in a total added options and packages value of $3,175, enhancing visibility, parking assistance, and open-air comfort while maintaining the Pacificas core balance of safety, flexibility, and all-weather capability

description:
Recent Arrival! 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Select 3.6L V6 24V VVT AWD CARFAX One-Owner.

This 2025 Chrysler Pacifica Select AWD is a versatile minivan designed to deliver confident all-weather capability, modern technology, and family-focused comfort. Finished in Bright White Clear-Coat with a black interior, this Pacifica presents a clean, contemporary appearance that pairs practical design with everyday usability.

Power comes from a 3.6L V6 paired with a 9-speed automatic transmission and an advanced all-wheel-drive system, providing smooth acceleration, confident traction, and added stability in changing road conditions. The AWD suspension works seamlessly with electronic stability control and advanced braking systems to support controlled driving year-round.

Inside, the cabin is engineered for flexibility and comfort. Caprice leatherette bucket seats are paired with second- and third-row Stow n Go seating, allowing quick transitions between passenger and cargo configurations. Heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, driver-seat memory, three-zone automatic climate control, and in-floor storage bins enhance daily convenience. Technology is centered around the Uconnect 5 system with a 10.1-inch touchscreen, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, SiriusXM capability, a 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot, and hands-free phone and audio integration.

Safety and driver-assist features are a core focus, with standard equipment including adaptive cruise control with stop and go, blind-spot monitoring with rear cross-path detection, lane-departure warning, full-speed forward-collision warning with pedestrian emergency braking, ParkSense rear park assist with stop, and a ParkView rear backup camera. Power sliding doors and a power liftgate add everyday ease for loading passengers and gear.

This Pacifica includes $1,280 in factory-added options, consisting of the Safety Sphere package, which adds a 360-degree surround-view camera system, front and rear park assist, and parallel and perpendicular park assist with stop, as shown on the original window sticker

Discover the ultimate family-friendly adventure with the stunning 2025 Kia Carnival SX. This exceptional minivan boasts a captivating design, unparalleled versatility, and a wealth of premium features that will elevate your driving experience.

Meticulously inspected and maintained, this Carnival SX is equipped with:

• 172 POINT SAFETY INSPECTION
• Aurora Black Pearl exterior
• Cross Bars
• EC Mirror w/HomeLink
• Carpeted Floor Mats (8-Passenger)
• Cargo Mat

Powered by a robust V6 engine and paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, this Carnival SX delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 18 city/26 highway MPG. The sleek and sophisticated exterior, complemented by the stunning Black color, exudes a commanding presence on the road.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin that seamlessly blends style and functionality. Enjoy the convenience of the Navigation System, the immersive sound of the 8-speaker audio system, and the comfort of the heated and ventilated front seats. The power driver's seat and power liftgate add to the overall ease of use, while the rear air conditioning and power moonroof enhance the overall driving experience.

Safety is paramount, and the Carnival SX delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Automatic Emergency Braking. You can drive with confidence, knowing your loved ones are well-protected.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or navigating the daily hustle and bustle, the 2025 Kia Carnival SX is the perfect companion. Its exceptional versatility, advanced features, and uncompromising safety make it the ideal choice for discerning buyers seeking the ultimate in modern minivan design.

Experience the difference for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional value and unparalleled capabilities of the 2025 Kia Carnival SX.

All prices include Alpine Down Payment Assistance of $1,000 financing credit and $689.50 dealer and handling.

The Carnival LX is packed with a wealth of features that will make your daily driving and family adventures more enjoyable. From the intuitive infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto to the rear air conditioning and power windows, this minivan is designed to keep you and your loved ones comfortable and connected on the road.

description:
This 2024 TOYOTA SIENNA XLE , has a GREY exterior and interior color with only 56,689 miles. Stock Number 2776. You can connect with us by calling 781-246-3331. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

For a quick, stress-free car buying experience you’ve come to the right place. At Salem Nissan we make the same pledge to all of our customers. We are proud of the products and services we sell, so there is no need for us to pressure you into buying. Those who pressure do so for a reason. As much as price, customers have always valued Salem Nissan's commitment to matters of social and community importance. Our reputations as an eco-responsible dealer, as well as leadership in caring for others is at the core of all we do. Our customer seek adventure, so when you need assistance, you can rely on Salem Nissan to be there to help. They call Service the "back end" but around here, our Service team is the heart. We stand behind everything we sell. It means there are no hidden fees in any transaction. A price quoted is a price we honor, and we will never quote a price using a rebated or incentive you do not qualify for. The Salem Nissan Mission Statement is unique. Two words: "To Serve." Our customers, our families, our community, and each other. It’s that simple. That’s why many of the things we do have nothing to do with selling cars. We do those things because it is the right thing to do. Our address is 93 S Broadway Salem NH 03079.

        Safety and Security
        • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
        • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
        • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
        • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
        Technology and Telematics
        • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
        Our certification process keeps you in mind every step of the way. The TCUV standards apply from the time a Toyota dealer acquires the vehicle through to the final sale. Each candidate for certification can be a current model year vehicle, up to and including 10-year-old models, with 120,000 miles or less on the odometer. Prior to the rigorous 160-point inspection, every certified Toyota goes through a CARFAX vehicle history report is reviewed to ensure that only the best of the best vehicles receive the Toyota Certified Seal of approval. Our industry-leading heritage also comes with exceptional coverage policies. Our TCUV Gold and Silver benefits allow you to drive with confidence! With TCUV Gold, you get a 12-month/12,000-mile Limited Comprehensive Warranty1 a 7-year/100,000-mile Limited Powertrain Warranty2 plus 24-Hour Roadside Assistance for 7 years/100,000 miles3, honored at more than 1,400 Toyota dealers in the U.S. and Canada and More!

The CarBravo Certified Used Vehicle Warranty, which is included at no extra cost, provides several benefits and features for eligible vehicles:
Vehicles must be up to 10 years old and have less than 100,000 miles.
A 12-month/12,000-mile limited bumper-to-bumper warranty is included. A 10-day/500-mile exchange policy allows you to swap your vehicle if you are not satisfied with your purchase.
Each vehicle undergoes a 126-point inspection.
The program also includes a 24-hour roadside assistance program, courtesy transportation, a vehicle history report, and trials for OnStar and SiriusXM.

• CarBravo Certified Used
• AUTOBUTLER PROTECTION APPLIED
• LEATHER
• NEW TIRES

Enjoy impressive fuel efficiency with an EPA-estimated 19 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway. The Odyssey's versatile interior offers seating for up to 8 passengers, plus ample cargo space for all your gear.

As a CarBravo Certified Used vehicle, this Odyssey has undergone a rigorous 126-point inspection and comes with a 12-month/12,000-mile limited bumper-to-bumper warranty. You can drive with confidence, knowing this Odyssey has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide years of reliable service.

The Honda Odyssey EX is packed with an impressive array of features, including:
• Leather-wrapped steering wheel
• Heated front seats
• Power driver's seat
• Dual-zone automatic climate control
• Rearview camera
• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System
• Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS)

Discover exceptional value with this 2023 Chrysler Voyager LX, now available in Griffin, GA. Inside, enjoy seamless smartphone integration with Android Auto, keeping navigation, music, and messages easily accessible. Stay connected with Hands Free Bluetooth for calls and audio streaming. Safety-forward technologies include Forward Collision Warning and a Back-Up Camera, enhancing visibility and helping prevent accidents while maneuvering in tight spaces. The Chrysler Voyager LX offers flexible seating and cargo capabilities, making it ideal for daily commutes, carpools, or weekend outings. Its comfortable cabin, straightforward controls, and durable construction make ownership straightforward and economical. Routine maintenance and a clean vehicle history mean you can buy with confidence. Located in Griffin, GA, this 2023 Chrysler Voyager LX is competitively priced and advertised as the best price in the area. Don't miss this opportunity to own a dependable, feature-rich minivan with the safety and connectivity features modern drivers expect. Contact us today to schedule a test drive or request more details.

This 2023 Chrysler Voyager features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. The Chrysler Voyager is pure luxury with a heated steering wheel. Good News! This certified CARFAX 1-owner vehicle has only had one owner before you. This Chrysler Voyager offers Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. If you’re looking for a local car dealership that offers new INFINITIs, used vehicles of all makes and models, exceptional service, and multiple finance options we’ve got you covered. Looking for used vehicles for sale in Oklahoma City? At Bob Moore INFINITI we have a large assortment of used vehicles including a variety of makes and models. While we carry many used makes and models, we also carry used INFINITIs in case you aren’t looking for new models. If you’re still trying to decide which model and trim is the best fit, we can get you with one of our certified INFINITI specialists to go over all the details — whether it’s regarding features, warranties, service, financing, or any other areas you’d like addressed. Our dealership also offers a variety of amenities, free Wi-Fi, and all kinds of perks. For those wishing to shop for their car online, we can help you with that as well. All our inventory is held on our website where you can complete the whole purchase process. If you’d like to visit the dealership but need assistance getting there, we offer free valet service within 30 minutes of our store and give free at-home delivery. If you need to schedule any of these services, please call our dealership.
When buying an used vehicle, we want to make sure you get your money’s worth. To ensure this, we put all our used vehicles through a service reconditioning process. This process includes a 106-point inspection of the vehicle to ensure that it’s up to our standards. We make sure the tires have three 30-second tire depths or 30%, if they don’t, we’ll replace the tires. We’ll also replace any brakes over 3mm. After the vehicles full inspection, it leaves the shop and goes through cosmetic refurbishing where we inspect and replace scratches, dents, scuffs, and road rash, as well as interior leather and upholstery reconditioning. While we work hard to ensure the quality of all used vehicles, we must acknowledge that some will end up with defects. Speak with one of our sales specialists about an used vehicle you’re interested in to get a history of the car. Bob Moore also covers all your INFINITI, and any other make or model, service needs with our factory trained technicians, including 4 master certified technicians. Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2018 Honda Odyssey Elite. This one-owner, CARFAX-verified vehicle has been meticulously maintained and is ready to take you and your family on countless adventures.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this Odyssey Elite is the epitome of modern family luxury. Key highlights include:
• Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System
• 11-Speaker Premium Audio System
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• Power Moonroof and Liftgate
• Blind Spot Information System
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto Integration

Vehicle Detailed

This Odyssey Elite has been meticulously cared for and is ready to provide you and your family with years of reliable and comfortable transportation. With its spacious interior, advanced safety features, and exceptional fuel efficiency, it's the perfect blend of practicality and sophistication.

Imagine the convenience of the power liftgate and the peace of mind that comes with the Blind Spot Information System. Enjoy the crystal-clear audio from the premium 11-speaker sound system as you navigate with the intuitive Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation. And with the heated and ventilated front seats, you'll arrive at your destination feeling refreshed and rejuvenated.

Beyond the impressive list of features, this Odyssey Elite also boasts a sleek and modern exterior design. The 19-inch alloy wheels and bold gray color scheme give it a striking presence on the road, while the power moonroof and fog lights add a touch of elegance.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and this Odyssey Elite delivers with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Collision Mitigation Braking System to the Lane Keeping Assist, you can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your loved ones are well-protected.

With its exceptional performance, unparalleled versatility, and comprehensive suite of features, this 2018 Honda Odyssey Elite is the perfect choice for discerning families. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident that this Odyssey will exceed your expectations and become the perfect companion for your daily adventures.

We are centrally located in beautiful LaGrange, Georgia just off interstate 85 at exit 18 - we proudly serve ALABAMA, FLORIDA, SOUTH CAROLINA & TENNESSEE. This 2018 Honda Odyssey EX-L, has a exterior and an interior color. 163,000 miles. Stock Number HT042853. You can connect with us by calling (706) 661-8751. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
At Mike Patton Honda, we're here to Serve you! Our staff is 100% dedicated to customer satisfaction and we understand that you need clear, transparent information throughout the car buying process. With our live market pricing philosophy, we offer the right cars at the right price, and the transparency to back it up!
